\id JHN NT0004.JN - Suena NT Wilson dp transfer 11-JUN-87
\h Yohane
\toc1 OZIGA EWANANA YOHANE MENI GAENUA
\toc2 Yohane
\mt1 OZIGA EWANANA YOHANE MENI GAENUA
\ip \it Yohane nu Yesura bua mai 12 amira zo. Nu Yesura uge ei awa zebu serora ema bama emo gaenua. Nu susu ego emira gaenua: Ema bama dapikarago meni Yesu gara Kristo me wai nu tuma didinoise nuai me ewanana tamarise. Are bua Yesu meni inoisonua kota, uge-mage inoisonua amira ge witai Yohane meni gaenua. \it*
\c 1
\s1 Yesu Anutura ge puro muro ema wero kei awenua.
\p 
\v 1 Bera ge* nu nuai gege noisonua. Bera ge nu Anutura nana giti mokara noisonua. Bera ge nu nutope Anutu.
\v 2 Nu awa gita susura ena Anuture dai nuai gege noisonua.
\v 3 Bera ge nu Anutura wana wero nena dapikarago wero tepo wenua. Ota nena kei awenua, awa nu tepo nena zo oko kei awenua.
\v 4 Ota wero nuai awa nuso nana itisonua. Are nuai awa emara nana zasimuro itisonua awa.
\v 5 Zasimai* ami mumera zasimunu mume meni zasimai siramu sero kaputinua, ata zasipitinowia awa.
\p 
\v 6 Anutu meni ema zo potinu kei awero noisonua zazo nuso Yohane.
\v 7 Nu ami zasimaira oziga samu munua. Ema bama dapikarago zasimaira Mama tuma diarise sero Anutu meni senu kei awenua awa.
\v 8 Yohane nu nutope zasimaira Mama oko aewa. Nu zasimaira oziga gege awa emare samu munua.
\p 
\v 9 Zasimai me nu ema bama dapikarago awa zasimai potitinowia ami be amire zebura kei awero noisonua.
\v 10 Nu zebura itisonua. Awa gege oko aewa. Zebu dai nune wenua awa. Ago wenua, ata zebura ema bama nukare nu oko giro baitiwa.
\v 11 Nu zebu nusora kei awenu dubu nuso meni nu giro gago-giago awewa.
\v 12 Ata eni meni awa nukare Yesu otao wewa, o Yesu tuma diwa ami Anutura mai awiso warise sero Yesu meni zazo nusokare senua awa.
\v 13 Nukare emara orarara ena oko kei awewa. Nukare emara ara tamaira kota, o emara sai zewai waira kota, nukare Anutura putoura kei awewa awa.
\p 
\v 14 Bera ge nu ema wero kei awero nasokare nana soe noisonua awa. Ago wenu nakare simai zasimaire nuso ginakare. Nu Anutura Mai me, are simai zasimaire nuso nana gege itisonua awa. Nuai me ata dumi yagaba awa duba nusora bera munu puro osenua awa.
\v 15 Susu nuso Yohane meni poti damu niro zawa sero ego senua awa, “Na nu amire sena awa, ‘Ama tupia ami nu gita wai naso inoya. Nera kota, na kaka kei awamure nu noisonua.’” Yohane meni ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 16 Nakai dapikarago ami dumi yagaba ewa-gaewa awa zamai nusora ena purota puro awinowenakai.
\v 17 Anutu meni lo ge namorekai potamu sero Mosere potinua awa. Ota Anutu meni dumi yagabare nuai mere awa namorekai potamu sero Yesu Kristore potinu puro munua awa.
\v 18 Anutu nu ema zo meni oko ginua. Tepo-tapo awa. Are Mai nuso daimata nuso nana zazene itima awinoya ami Mama nuso namorekai kereninua awa.
\s1 Yohane ge ou gutai zaawai ema ami Yesura ge kereninua.
\p 
\v 19 Yuda ema meni Yerusalem ena pris enire wana soga enire sewa bamuro Yohane atata wero ego sewa awa, “Ni ema aweni?”
\v 20 Ago sewa Yohane nu susu nuso kaka bezamu kereniro ego senua awa, “Na Soyai Ema nisokare Kristo tepo.”
\v 21 Ago senu nukare noko atata wero ego sewa awa, “Ina ni aweni? Ni Elia, Kristora awi mai ni?” Ago sewa nu ego senua awa, “Na Elia tepo.” Ago senu nukare ego sewa awa, “Ni porofete dia inowenakare awa ni?” Ago sewa nu ego senua awa, “Tepo awa.”
\v 22 Ago senu nukare noko atata wero ego sewa awa, “Ina ni aweni? Nakare baro ema babezinoma nakare sesera menakare amire nogo samunonikare? Ni nitope nogo towesi?”
\v 23 Ago sewa nu ina ego senua awa, “Porofete Yesaya meni ge zo gaenua awa naso nana ena me inoya. Na oziga sai ema ware gamu-gamura ena noise ego towena awa, ‘Tuara ebata kora weu sonae.’” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 24 Ema Yohane nana muwa awa Farisayo meni potiwa muwa awa.
\v 25 Are nukare nu noko atata wero ego sewa awa, “Ni Soyai Ema nasokare Kristo-ko sia, o Elia-ko sia, o porofete-ko sia ago tosa agiyo. Are ni nogoro ema bama ge ou gutinosi?”
\v 26 Ago sewa Yohane meni ina ego senua awa, “Na ema ou gege gutinona awa. Ota nisokare nana ena zo kei awamunoya, nikare nu oko gosinowewa.
\v 27 Nune naso nana atune mamunoya ami ema bamubake awa. Na ema osai me osai ami sandol* nusora asi besai ine te oko inoya.” Ago senua awa.
\v 28 Susu awa nata zazo Betani, ou Yodan enibara itisonua, amira ana kei awenua. Yohane meni ago noise ana ema bama ge ou gutinoisonua awa.
\s1 Yohane meni Yesu nu Anutura lama asenua.
\p 
\v 29 Pina atinu Yesu meni Yohane nana susaunu aikera ena giro ego senua awa, “Ou giu. Anutura lama. Nune ami zebu serora pasina nusokare dimuro betamunoya.
\v 30 Na nu amire sena awa, ‘Ama mamunoya nu ami gita wai naso inoya. Nera kota, na kaka kei awamure nu noisonua awa.’ Numa owa.
\v 31 Na natope nu gita oko gina kei awenua. Ata Isreli ema nikare oziga nuso sana ninawise sero na kei awero ge ou zaawena.”
\p 
\v 32 Yohane meni emare ge ago sero senua awa, “Ozana meni ni guma ine wero utura ena osero nuso nana arumuro iti goisena.
\v 33 Na gita nu oko gina kei awenua, ata Anutu meni nane ema bama ge ou gutanise sero ego senua awa, ‘Ozana osero nuso nana arumuro itai ema ami ge sai amire ema bama Ozana pumamunora.’
\v 34 Are nama ana susu nuso giro ego tona ewa: Nu Anutura Mai me awa.” Yohane meni ge ago senua awa.
\s1 Yesu meni bua mai zoeto-zoeto pumunua.
\p 
\v 35 Pina atinu Yohane ata bua mai nuso eto ami dopero itiwa
\v 36 Yesu tupinu giro Yohane meni ego senua awa, “Anutura lama owa.”
\v 37 Ago senu bua mai nuso eto meni ge awa niniro Yesura nana ama bamuwato awa.
\v 38 Bamuwato Yesu meni kapeteniro giro numoreto ego senua awa, “Nito ne kau inowito?” Ago senu nuto ego sewato awa, “Rabai, (Ge nasokaira, “Gipai ema”) ni so nera itesi?”
\v 39 Ago sewato Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Muuto gaweto.” Ago senu mai eto meni nu ama ganero sora witiwato awa. Witiroto waiko be da numore dai itiwato. Awa waiko diti osisinoinu 4 klok wenua, are ago wewato awa.
\p 
\v 40 Nuto Yohanera ge niniro Yesu ama ganewato amira zo zazo nuso Anderea. Nu Simon Petorora nami.
\v 41 Anderea nu nami nuso Simon eya tamuro ego senua awa, “Nato Yuda emara Soyai Ema zazo Mesia awa tamenato.” (Mesia awa Kristo).
\v 42 Ago sero Yesura nana uzumunu baro kei awewato Yesu meni Petoro giro ego senua awa, “Zazo niso Simon. Ni Yohanera mai. Ata na zazo niso seka Sifas asinona awa.” (Ge nasokaira, “Omata Arama”) Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 43 Pina atinu Yesu nu Galilaya zebura bayamu sero eriro Filip tamuro ego senua awa, “Ni na ama gane.” Ago senua awa.
\v 44 Filip nu Besaida natara. Andereato Petorore nuto dai nata da amira.
\v 45 Are Filip meni Nataniel tamuro ego senua awa, “Ema Mose meni lo gera ge nuso gaenua, o porofete eni meni da ago gaewa, ema awa tamenakare. Nu Yesu, Yosefera mai. Nu Nasarete natara awa.”
\v 46 Ago senu Nataniel meni ge ina ego senua awa, “Nena kokopai zo meni Nasarete nate ena kei awai te inoita?” Ago senu Filip meni ina ego senua awa, “Ago tosaya mu baro gase.”
\p 
\v 47 Ago senu Nataniel nu Yesu nana bamunu Yesu meni giro ego senua awa, “Ei giu. Ema ei awa Isreli ema me. Ge opi sai duba nusora tepo.”
\v 48 Ago senu Nataniel meni Yesu atata wero ego senua awa, “Ni nogo nogo wero susu naso gosinosi?” Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Filip meni ni kaka tamamure nane ni ni fik susura itesa gena awa.”
\v 49 Ago senu Nataniel meni ina ego senua awa, “Gipai ema, ni Anutura Mai me. Ni Isreli emara ema tua.”
\v 50 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Ni fik susura itesa giro sesena amira gege na tuma didinosua. Tani zeme gesa awa osino gege. Ata ama nena me bamu kei awero bayai gosinuamunosa.”
\v 51 Ago sero numore ego senua awa, “Na me memeka sane. Nikare utu be zaumai amire Anutura angelo dubu meni na Emara Mai amira nana witiro osero awara gamunowa awa.” Ago senua awa.
\c 2
\s1 Yesu meni senu ou meni wain wenua.
\p 
\v 1 Waiko be eto tepo wenu Galilaya zebura nata zo zazo Kena amira ana ema zo bama ataise amira nena asa-waura wewa mu nate ninu Yesura mia dai ago itinua.
\v 2 Yesu ata bua mai nuso nukare dai aunarise sewa giro baro auniwa awa.
\v 3 Auniro itise ou wain niwa tepo wenu giro Yesura mia meni numore ego senua awa, “Ou wain nusokare tepo wetia.”
\v 4 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na nukare soremamunona asero tosita? Amira be naso kaka mamu.”
\v 5 Ago senu amire mia nuso meni soumaire ego senua awa, “Yesu meni bua zo wawise sai giro ge nuso dimuwo.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 6 Are so amira au babezinoma 6 ago itiwa awa. Yuda emara nana so sero au ago ine itasai amire nukare ewowora tani inoise nenare tamare sewinoisowa. Au awa babezinoma. Au daimata amira ou pake 10 meni niginoisowa.
\v 7 Are Yesu meni soumaire ego senua awa, “Nikare ou dumuro aura zozeu bera mare.” Ago senu soumai meni ou dumuro aura zozewa bera muwa awa.
\v 8 Ago wewa amire nu ego senua awa, “Nikare ou aura awa eni dumuro bonara mamera nana puro bamuu.” Ago senu giro puro bamuwa awa.
\v 9 Dumuro puro bonara mamera nana susauwa ou wain wenua awa. Puro bamuwa bonara mama meni ninu be zozowa wenua. Ago wenu nu ou wain awa nana munu amira susu nu kaka gamu, ata soumai ou dumuwa ami giwa. Are bonara mama meni ema bama atitinoinua awa zawa senu munu
\v 10 ego senua awa, “Gita ou wain me potawenakare nawera duba sirawi amire ou wain zuma osai awa ama potawenakare ninowera. Tani nasokare ago itia awa. Ata nine meni awa ou wain me bezero ou wain zuma osai gita potesa nera amire me ama puro potitinosa.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 11 Yesu nu Kena nate Galilaya zebura ana tani putoure nuso gita zaawero tani awa wenua awa. Ago wero nu putou nuso kereninu bua mai nuso meni tani putoure awa giro nu tuma diwa awa.
\s1 Yesu nu Anutura ibu bamu awa saramai asenua.
\p 
\v 12 Ataira bona tepo wenu Yesu nu Kena nate ena bamu Kapaneam nate namu inoinu mia nuso namisinire ata bua mai nuso nukare dai bamuwa awa. Baro ago be dainiro oko noiwa.
\v 13 Yuda emara pura zo zazo nuso Betai Daininua amira be zora awenu giro Yesu meni Yerusalem witiro bamunua awa.
\v 14 Yerusalem nate kei awero Anutura ibu bamu amira baro osi zora ena lama ata bulimakao ata ni guma awa puro baro ina-pota inoise noiwa ginua. Noko eni meni moni tebol tame potiro moni ina-pota inoise itiwa awa.
\v 15 Ago inoiwa giro Yesu meni asi tenero ami lama bulimakao emare tunenu bamuwa tebol monire ziro kapeteninu moni ose dura ninua awa.
\v 16 Ago wero ema ni guma puro dopero itiwa amire ego senua awa, “Puro bamuu. Nikare Mama nasora ibura ena nena ina-pota wawa stoa ibu ine wai azu tona.” Ago senua awa.
\v 17 Yesu ago wenu bua mai nuso meni ge zo gayai itewia awa kotumuwa. Ge awa ego ewa,
\li2 Ibu niso emi emo tini naso kapinoya.
\p 
\v 18 Are Yuda ema meni Yesu atata wero ego sewa awa, “Ai meni sesi tani awa wetesi? Anutu meni sai wamesa sia, awa susu awa poti damu namu sero tani putoure zo we ganekare.”
\v 19 Ago sewa Yesu meni be nusokarera pumuro ina ego senua awa, “Nikare ibu ei awa ziwawa nane waiko be etorobara gege eya wana noko dopamunoya.”
\v 20 Ago senu nukare ego sewa awa, “Mamana nasokare meni ibu ei awa zepa 46 ago gapinoe pesuniwa, awa nine waiko be etorobara gege wasa dopaise tosa?” Ago sewa awa.
\p 
\v 21 Ata Yesu nu tama aiso nusora ge awa ibu bamura potiro senua awa.
\v 22 Are ama noe betero betaira ena seka wero erinu amire bua mai nuso meni ge awa kotumuwa awa. Ago kotupitinoise Anutura ge gayai eni amire ge Yesu meni senua amire awa giwa me wenua.
\p 
\v 23 Yesu meni Yerusalem itise pura amira ana tani putoure eni wenu ema dainiro meni tani putoure awa giro Yesu tuma diwa awa.
\v 24 Yesu nu nutope emara moka gosinoise susu nuso numorekare kaka kerenamu wenua.
\v 25 Nu ema zora susu gamu sero ema eni oko atata inoisonua. Nu nutope emara kotumai giro baititinoisonua awa.
\c 3
\s1 Nikodemora uge.
\p 
\v 1 Ema zo noisonua zazo nuso Nikodemo. Nu Farisayo zo. Nu Yuda emara gita wai bamubake noisonua awa.
\v 2 Ema ami pire Yesu nana baro ego senua awa, “Gipai ema, nakare susu niso gosinowenakare. Ni gipai ema me meni Anutura bera mutasa. Ni tani inowesa awa ema zo meni Anutu tepo noise wai ine oko itia.”
\p 
\v 3 Ago senu Yesu meni ina numore ego senua awa, “Na me memeka sana gi. Zo nu kei awai seka noko kaka kei awamu wamunoya, awa nu Anutura nata gai ine tepo wamunoya.”
\v 4 Ago senu Nikodemo meni ina ego senua awa, “Zo nu zai wai meni nogo wero amire kei awai seka kei awamunoi? Nu miera tinira noko toyai amire pumai te oko inoi, tanita?”
\v 5 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na me memeka sana gi. Zo nu oura ata Ozanara putou amira kaka kei awamu wamunoya, awa nu Anutura nate bayai ine tepo wamunoya.
\v 6 Zo nu mia meni pumai awa zebura tama aisore dai nowia. Ata zo nu Ozana meni pumai awa Ozanare dai nowia.
\v 7 Nikare kei awai seka kei awawise sesena awa niniro di oko tainase.
\v 8 Bisi nu tebe-tabe tupewia, ata ni awi nuso gege ninitinowesa, o susu nana zaawero tupi, o baro nana tepo inoi, awa ni oko gosinowesa. Da ago ine zo nu Ozana meni pumai amira susu ni oko gosinowesa.”
\v 9 Ago senu Nikodemo meni ina ego senua awa, “Tani awa nogo nogo wero kei awamunoi?”
\v 10 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Ni Isreli emara gipai ema meni tani awa kaka gamu ni?
\v 11 Na me memeka sane. Nakare nena kotumai meni gosinowenakare, o nena giti moka meni goisenakare da awa towenakare awa. Ago wawenakare amire nikare ge nasokare dotinowewa awa.
\v 12 Nena zebura kei awinowia awa sawena gawewa me kaka wamu inowia ami utura nena itia awa sana nogo nogo wero gawa me wamunoi?
\v 13 Ema zo meni utura witiro noe oko osenua. Na Emara Mai imata utura ena osena. Nane gege imata utura nena gosinona.
\v 14 Mose meni gita ware ena kapa puro zi kewero puro witiro ni pasinaira ikoninua, da ago ine na Emara Mai ni pasinaira witanise sai itia.
\v 15 Are na tuma diamunora ami nuai me ewanana awa tamamunora.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 16 Zo nu Anutura Mai tuma diamunoya ami betaise kota, nu nuai me ewanana tamaise sero Anutu meni ema nakai emo duba bayao bamubake inoise Mai nuso daimata potinu osenua awa.
\v 17 Anutura Mai meni ema gera potaise kota, ema soyaise sero Anutu meni senu osenua awa.
\v 18 Zo nu Anutura Mai tuma diamunoya ami Anutura kotora ena oko duwamunoya. Zo nu Anutura Mai kaka tuma diamu wamunoya nu ami kotora ena emoko duwia ago ine wamunoya. Nera kota, nu Anutura Mai daimata awa kaka tuma diamu inoya.
\v 19 Are kotora ena duwai amira susu ego itia awa. Zasimai meni zebura kei awenu ema nukare zasimaira bayai azu sero mumera dago itamu sewa awa. Nukare nuai nusokare waya, are ago wewa awa.
\v 20 Zo nu pasina inowia ami zasimai azu inowia. Zasimai meni pasina nusora susu kerenai azu inoise nu zasimaira oko kei awamunoya.
\v 21 Nukare ge me niniro puro nowera ami zasimaira kei awinowera awa. Zo nu zasimaira kei awawi zasimai meni bua nusora susu kerenawi ema bama meni giro bua nusora me awa Anutura putoura kei awinowia, ago samunora awa.
\s1 Yohane meni Yesura susu kereninua.
\p 
\v 22 Yesu meni bua mai nuso pumunu Yerusalem doro Yudaya zebu agewara baro noisowa. Ago noise amire ema eni ge ou gutenua.
\v 23 Yohane dai ema bama ge ou gutinoise itinua. Nu zebu zo zazo Ainon, Selim nate kena ago noise ge ou gutai bua inoisonua. Nu zebu amira ana inoisonua, nera kota, ou bamu ago itisonua. Are ema bama nuso nana kokounasara ge ou gutinoisonua awa.
\v 24 Yohane nu be amire Herode meni benai sora kaka potamu noise bua awa inoisonua awa.
\p 
\v 25 Are Yuda ema zo ata Yohanera bua mai nukare tama aiso sewaira tani amira ge ina-sa wewa awa.
\v 26 Ge tomite bua mai meni bamu Yohane nana niro ego sewa awa, “Gipai ema, ni ou Yodan enibara ena nosa ema zo ni tami susu nuso kereniro namorekare sisesa. Ema ami be zeme emire ema bama ge ou gutinoise iti giro dapikarago nuso nana susawera.”
\v 27 Ago sewa Yohane meni ego senua awa “Ema zo nu utura Mama meni nena numore kaka potamu wai nu nutope nena awa pai ine tepo.
\v 28 Na ego toise nimorekare sesena goisewa awa, ‘Na Kristo oko aewa. Anutu meni na potinu nane ebata nuso gita inona.’
\v 29 Ema zo bama atamunoya bama awa nuso gege awa.* Are nu yawa sara inuai otao nuso meni zorage dopero ge nuso niniro da ago duba kokopai wamunoya. Ema bama meni Yesura nana bamitara, are duba kokopai waira be naso kei awitaya.
\v 30 Nune witai gege wititinuamunoya. Ata nane meni awa osamunona.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 31 Ike ena osenua ami witai nasokai awa. Zo nu zebura ena kei awai ami zebu emira, are nu zebura ge towia. Ota utura ena osenua ami nakai dapikarago dainiro bamu nasokai wero nowia awa.
\v 32 Nune utura nena gosinoisonua awa namorekai kereniro towia, ata ema meni ge nuso dotinowera.
\v 33 Zo nu Maira ge niniro puro poti dube niro nowia ami ago inoise “Anutu ge me towia,” asinowia.
\v 34 Ema Anutu meni senu osenua ami Anutura ge towia. Nera kota, Anutu meni Ozana zere dago numore potai gege potitinowia.
\v 35 Mama nu Mai nuso ara tapinoise nena bamubamu dapikarago Maira nana wanera potinu itewera.
\v 36 Zo nu Anutura Mai tuma didinowia ami nuai me ewanana puro nowia. Ata zo nu Anutura Mai amira ge dero nowia ami nuai me ewanana oko gamunoya. Ema ago amira nana Anutura tini kapai meni itai gege itamunoya.
\c 4
\s1 Yesuto Samaria bama zore ge uge wewato.
\p 
\v 1 Farisayo nukare Yesura oziga ego niniwa awa, “Yesu nu ema dainiro puro ge ou gutinoya, are bua mai dubu nuso meni Yohanera bua mai dubu awa dainitinoya.” Ago niniwa awa.
\v 2 Ata Yesu nu nutope ema zo ge ou kaka gutamu. Bua mai nuso meni ema bama ge ou gutinoisowa awa.
\v 3 Are Farisayo ge ago ine niniwa giro Yesu meni Yudaya zebu doro ewesemuro Galilaya zebura bamunua awa.
\v 4 Ebata awa Samaria zebu busero susawisonua.
\p 
\v 5 Yesu meni zebu awa busero susaumite Samaria nata zo zazo Saika amira kei awenua awa. Nata awa Yakobo meni mai nuso Yosefere zebu agewa potinua amira zorage itisonua awa.
\v 6 Ota zebu da amira Yakobora ou ura wamai zo itisonua. Are Yesu nu ago kei awero waiko soe dopenua, are putou tepo wenu giro ou ura wamai amira zorage arumunua awa.
\v 7 Arumuro itinu Samaria bama zo ou dumamu sero munua. Munu Yesu meni giro numore ego senua awa, “Ou poti nane.” Ago senua awa.
\v 8 Bua mai nuso nukare ma pumamu sero nate witiwa nu imata itimite bamere oura ge senua awa.
\v 9 Senu bama meni numore ego senua awa, “Ni Yuda ema meni nogoro ou emo Samaria bama namore ge tosi?” Ago senua, nera kota, Yuda emare Samaria emare nukare kapero noisowa, are bama meni ge awa senua.
\v 10 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Ni Anutu dumi pai nusora susure, o ou emo tona amira susure gamesa, awa ni ou emo namore begomo sasa na nuai me ewanana amira ou awa nimore potamena.”
\v 11 Ago senu bama meni ina ego senua awa, “Ou ura awa tura me tura. Agoro ni kopi ou dumai tepo. Are nuai me ewananara ou awa nana pamunosi?
\v 12 Ewowo nasokai Yakobo nu ou ura ei awa wamunua. Ago wenu nu ata mai awiso nuso ata lama bulimakao nukare dapikarago ami ou ei awa ninoise noisowa. Nu ou ura ei awa namorekai dirieninua. Ata ni Yakobo dainitinosa, ago tosita?”
\v 13 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Ou ei awa nawewa noko ou uza eya inowia.
\v 14 Ata ou nane potamunona awa zo meni nai ou uza noko oko wamunoya. Nane ou awa ema zore potana duba nusora ena ou kupi-kupi inuamunoya. Ago inuai ema ami nuai me ewanana puro nuamunoya.”
\v 15 Ago senu bama meni ego senua awa, “Ema, ni ou awa potasa niro ou uza kaka wamu nuane. Ago wero ou emo eyaya ego tupewena awa duane.”
\p 
\v 16 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Ni baro ema niso puro maweto.”
\v 17 Ago senu bama meni ina ego senua awa, “Na ema tepo.” Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Ni ema niso tepo awa me tosa awa.
\v 18 Ni ema wana da ago atiro doro awinowesa. Agoro be zeme ewa ni ema zore nosa, ata nu ema niso tepo, are ni ge me tosa.”
\v 19 Ago senu bama meni ego senua awa, “Ema, na zeme susu niso gosinona. Ni porofete me.
\v 20 Are se gane. Zezewenai nasokare nukare dirumu emira* ena auniro Anutura yere gapise ge ninise awinoisowa. Ata Yuda ema ninekare meni awa Yerusalem nate ena Anutu isa sise yere gapise awinoise nuanisekai sai itia ago towewa.”
\p 
\v 21 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Bama, na ge sana gasa me wae. Be zo zorage awinoya. Be awa kei awai amire nikare Mama isare yerere meni bowi wamu sero dirumu emirata Yerusalem nate ena oko wamunowa.
\v 22 Ninekare awa kaka giro baitamu inoise yere isare towewa. Nanekare awa giro baititinoise yere isare towenakare. Nera kota, korawai ewanana wai awa Yudara nana ena gita kei awaise sai itia.
\v 23 Be zo mamunoya be amire Anutura ema dubu me meni nu bowi wamu sero ititire tani mere meni wamunora. Mama nu ema ago ine ami nu bowi warise yaba inowia.
\v 24 Anutu nu tama aiso kota, nu ititi. Are nikare nu bowi wamu sero tama meni kota, ititire tani mere meni nu bowi inoise noiwo.”
\v 25 Ago senu bama meni ina ego senua awa, “Na gosinona. Mesia zazo nuso zo Kristo ami mamunoya. Nu muro nena dapikarago poti damu namunoya.”
\v 26 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Ge tosa awa zo tepo, ata na ewa nimore dai ge tona. Ge awa nama awa.”
\p 
\v 27 Ge ago toinu bua mai nuso kei awewa. Kei awero bamere dai ge toiwato awa giro di tainiwa awa. Ota nena ne emo bamere ge toi, o nogoro toi, ago sero atata waira awa giwa te kaka wamu wenu giro dowa awa.
\v 28 Ago wewa bama nu kopi ou dumai nuso doro sumuro bamu nate niro emare senua awa,
\v 29 “Nikare muu. Baro ema zo gawe. Nune nuai nasora susu dapikarago namore kerenia. Nu Kristo, tanita?”
\v 30 Ago senu ema dago Yesu gamu bamuwa awa.
\p 
\v 31 Nukare Yesura nana susauwa bua mai nuso meni Yesure ego sewa awa, “Gipai ema, ni nena ni.”
\v 32 Ago sewa ina ego senua awa, “Ma naso itia. Awa nikare oko gosinowa.”
\v 33 Ago senu bua mai nuso meni nutopekare ina-sa wero sewa awa, “Ai meni ma puro mi?”
\v 34 Ago sewa giro nu ego senua awa, “Nu na potinu muna amira ge dimuro bua nuso wero susauma pesunamunona ami ma naso inoya awa.
\v 35 Nikare nitopekare ego towewa awa, ‘Inua zoeto-zoeto ago tepo wai amire ma me wamunoya.’ Are nane sana niniu. Nikare irina-arina wero bua giu. Ma pumaira be* kei awero itia.
\v 36 Ema zo nu ma puro poti dara nai bua inoya ami zuma pupinoya. Nu ma nuai me ewananara gegenai awa pumu sora nitinoya. Are ema ma urai ema ata ema ma pumai ema nuto ami eroma yawa sara wamunorato.
\v 37 Are ge ego towenakai ami ena me inoya, ‘Zo meni urai bua inowia, ota zo meni pumai bua inowia.’
\v 38 Ma nikare kaka uramu wisewa amira me awa pumu sora nawise sesena bayamunowa. Bua awa eni meni wisera amira me ninekare pumamunowa.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 39 Are Samaria ema bama dainiro meni bamera ge niniro Yesu tuma diwa awa. Ago wewa, nera kota, bama meni nuai nusora susu awa dapikarago Yesu meni kereninu giro ema bama susure senu niniwa.
\v 40 Are nukare Yesura nana muro Yesu numorekare dai nuaise uzumuro puro bamu nate namu sewa giro Yesu meni numorekare dai waiko be eto ago noinua awa.
\v 41 Ago noise ge toise noinu ema dainiro meni ge nuso niniro nu tuma diwa.
\v 42 Ago wero bamere ego sewa awa, “Gita nakare uge niso niniro nu tuma dienakare. Ota zeme ei awa nakare be so nusora ena ge niniro ego tonakare: Nu zebu serora ema bama amira Korawai Ema me.” Ago sewa awa.
\s1 Yesu meni ge senu mai zora yaya tepo wenua.
\p 
\v 43 Yesu nu Samaria emare dai be eto itimite nukare doro Galilaya zebura bamunua awa.
\v 44 Yesu nu ge gita ego senua awa, “Porofete nukare nata nusokarera kei awero ema zazore oko inowera.”
\v 45 Are Yesu meni Galilaya zebura baro kei awenu Galilaya ema nu giro areniro yawa sara wewa. Awa nera kota, be zore nukare bamu Yerusalem niro Yuda emara pura amira ana bua Yesu meni wenua awa giwa.
\p 
\v 46 Yesu meni Galilaya zebura kei awero Kena nate bamunua. Nata amira ana nu gita ge senu ou meni wain wenua. Ago bamunu Kapaneam nate dia ema bamu zo noisonua amira mai yaya mou-mau puro itinua.
\v 47 Are “Yesu nu Yudaya zebu doro ewesemuro mu Galilaya zebura niro noya,” ago sewa giro dia ema ami bamu Kena nate niro Yesura nana bamunua awa. Baro mai nuso betamu sero inoinu giro Yesu uzumuro puro sora baro mai nuso kora waise senua.
\v 48 Ago senu Yesu meni numore ego senua awa, “Nikare tani putoure eni ata bua bamu eni awa kaka gamu wamunowa, awa nikare na oko tuma diamunowa.”
\v 49 Ago senu dia ema meni ego senua awa, “O Tua, mai naso betai azu, eya bayasise tona.”
\v 50 Ago senu Yesu meni numore ego senua awa, “Ni tepo bamu. Mai niso ewanana wetia awa.” Ago senu dia ema nu Yesura ge nininu me wenu giro bamunua awa.
\v 51 Ewesemuro susaunu soumai nuso eni meni oziga puro muro nu tamuro ego sewa awa, “Mai niso ewanana wero noya.”
\v 52 Ago sewa giro mai ewanana wenua amira waiko be awa gamu sero atata wenu sewa awa, “Awenakai amire waiko soe dopero iti amire tama mena-mana nuso tepo wataya.”
\v 53 Ago sewa dia ema meni susu ego ginua awa: “Be amire Yesu meni na ewesemanise sero ego sasaya, ‘Mai niso ewanana wetia.’” Are dia ema meni susu awa giro nu arere awisore Yesu tuma diwa awa.
\v 54 Yesu Yudaya zebura ena ewesemuro Galilaya zebura kei awero tani awa wenua, awa tani putoure namba tu Galilaya zebura ena wenua awa.
\c 5
\s1 Yesu nu Betesida ou butura ena ema zo kora wenua.
\p 
\v 1 Yuda emara pura zo amira be munu giro Yesu witiro bamu Yerusalem ninua awa.
\v 2 Goma zo nata Yerusalem zimai amira toyai be zo zazo nuso Lama Toyai Be. Toyai be amira ou butu zo itisonua zazo nuso Yuda gera Betesida. Ou amira bera bisi paira so wana da ago itisowa.
\v 3 So amira ema yayare witai ami duro itisowa. Ema eni giti guma wai, o eni zabura wai, o eni orara touwai dainiro meni ago itisowa. [Nukare ou pasi wai gamu dia itisowa.
\v 4 Ago itasara be enire Tuara angelo zo meni osero ou butu dasai pasi wasai yaya emara nana zo meni gita gita wero ose oura niro dagimasai yaya nuso eya tepo wasai ewanana inoisonua awa.]
\v 5 Are ema zo nu zabura wero noe donu zepa 38 wenua ami ago itinua.
\v 6 Yesu meni ema awa giro yaya nuso borere-barere itisonua awa giro numore ego senua awa, “Ni ewanana wamu kotupitinosita?”
\v 7 Ago senu ema zebura wai ami ina ego senua awa, “O ema, ou pasi wai amire ai meni na wana ziro pumai osero ou awa dagimuro ewanana wamunoni? Eni meni na dainiro ose oura nawera giro na itewena.”
\v 8 Ago senu Yesu meni ina numore ego senua awa, “Ni eriro sawa niso puro aita we.”
\v 9 Ago senu ema zebura waira tama kokopai wenu nu eriro sawa nuso pumuro aita wenua awa. Waiko be awa Yuda emara Sabat pura itiwa awa.
\p 
\v 10 Are Yuda ema meni ema ewanana wenua amire ego sewa awa, “Pura be emira sai zewai wai ge nasokai itia awa ni dainitinoise sawa masi niso puro nosa, atonua.”
\v 11 Ago sewa nu ina ego senua awa, “Na kora wetia ami ego sesia awa, ‘Sawa niso puro aita we.’”
\v 12 Ago senu sewa awa, “Sawa niso puro aita we, ago ema zazo ai meni sesi?”
\v 13 Ago sewa ema senu kokopai wenua ami Yesura zazo kau wenua. Nera kota, Yesu nu ema dubu dopero itiwa amira nana soe ena saitiro bamunua awa.
\v 14 Ama Yesu meni ema awa Anutura ibu bamura ena tamuro ego senua awa, “Ni tama niso ewanana watasa, ata mou-mau zo niso nana kei awai azu, pasina doro noiyo.”
\v 15 Ago senu nu Yesu giro baitiro bamuro Yuda emare ego senua awa, “Ema na kora wetia awa zazo nuso Yesu.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 16 Yesu nu Sabat pura amire bua ago ine wenua, are Yuda ema meni giro nu iwo wewa awa.
\v 17 Ago wewa Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Mama naso nu bua wai gege inoise nowia, are na da ago ine bua inona.” Ago senua awa.
\v 18 Yesu nu Sabat pura sisenua, ota Anutu nu Mama nuka nuso asinoise nu Anutu ine awa senua, awa Yuda ema meni giwa waya wenu giro nukare Yesu damu sero ebata tamamu wewa.
\s1 Yesu meni nakai awa-uzai eranakai amire nu kotora zas wamunoya.
\p 
\v 19 Ago sewa Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na me memeka sana niniu. Na Mai meni duba nasora bua oko inowena. Mama meni wawi giro inowena. Mama meni wawi giro na Mai meni da ago inowena.
\v 20 Mama nu Mai nuso giro yaba dasiga inowia, are bua inowia awa te gipinowia. Ota bua ei awa gege kota, bua witai eni itera awa dai Maire gipai giro nikare titibi awero di tainamunowa awa.
\v 21 Mama nu betai ema awa-uzawi seka inowera, da ago ine na Mai meni ara tamai nasora zota zo awa-uzana seka wamunora awa.
\v 22 Mama nu emara zas oko inowia. Bua awa dapikarago Maira nana wanera potinua awa.
\v 23 Are ema nukare Mama bowi inowera, da ago ine Mai bowi warise. Zo nu Mai bowi kaka wamu wamunoya ami Mama na iyetinua awa dai bowi kaka wamu ago ine inoya.
\p 
\v 24 Na me memeka sana niniu. Zo meni ge naso ninitinoise Mama naso na iyetinua amira ge gi me inoya ami nuai me ewanana zeme emire puro noya. Nu kotora ena oko duwamunoya. Nu zewai wero betai doro nuaira kei awero nowia.
\p 
\v 25 Na me memeka sana niniu. Ema bama nowera ami bebetenai ine. Be zo mamunoya — ota kei awero itia — be amire nukare Anutura Mai amira ge awi ninamunora. Eni meni ge niniro baitiro seka wero nuamunora awa.
\v 26 Mama nu nuaira Mama, are nu Mai nusore da ago nuai dirieninu na nuaira Mama wero nowena.
\v 27 Na Mai, na Emara Mai. Are Mama naso meni emara koto amira zas bua awa na Mamera bera wanise sero putou namore potinua.
\v 28 Nikare ge awa niniro oko di tainawe. Nera kota, be zo potai itia awa mai amire bi ditira awinowera ami zawa naso ninamunora.
\v 29 Ago niniro ewanana noisowa ami eriro nuai me ewanana tamamunora. Ota waya wero noisowa ami meni awa eriro koto wero kotora ena duwamunora awa.
\v 30 Na duba nasora bua zo wai ine oko itia. Na ge Mama nasora bera ena ninitinowena da awa inoise kotora zas inowena awa. Ago inoise kotora zas bua wana te wamunoya. Nera kota, na ara tamai nasora kota, nu senu osena amira ara tamaira wamu inowena awa.
\s1 Anutu meni Mai nusora susu kerenitinowia.
\p 
\v 31 Na natope susu naso sana te oko wamunoya.
\v 32 Susu naso awa zo meni kerenitinowia. Nu susu naso kerenitinoise ge me toya awa gosinona.
\v 33 Nikare sesewa bua mai nisokare meni Yohanera nana baro atata wetera nu ge me kereniro sisia awa.
\v 34 Ema zo meni susu naso kerenaise awa oko yaba inona. Nikare susu naso ninawa Anutu meni nikare soero pumaise sero nimorekare sesena awa.
\v 35 Yohane nu zasimai bamubake ine wero noise nikare zasimunua. Zasimai nuso giro yawa sara apunu-kaka gege inoise noisewa awa.
\v 36 Ata susu naso kerenitinowia ami nu Yohane ine oko aewa. Nu witai. Na bua Mama meni wanise senua awa inowena. Bua ami susu naso ego ine kerenitinowia: Mama meni senu osena awa.
\v 37 Are Mama na senu osena ami susu naso kerenitinowia. Nikare be nusora ge kaka ninamu inowewa. Nikare giti moka nuso kaka gamu inowewa.
\v 38 Ge nuso duba nisokarera oko itia. Nera kota, nikare Mama na senu osena amira ge ninawewa me kaka wamu inowia.
\v 39 Nikare ego towewa awa, ‘Anutura ge gayai ami nuai me ewanana namorekai tamamunoya.’ Ago toise nuai me ewanana tamamu sero ge gayai azipitinowewa. Ge gayai ami susu naso kerenitinowia,
\v 40 ata nikare na nuai me ewanana nimorekare potanise sero namore dai dara tayai azu towewa.
\v 41 Ema meni na bowi warise oko towena.
\v 42 Na susu nisokare gosinowena. Duba nisokare meni awa Anutu Mama nasora nana oko itewia.
\v 43 Na Mama nasora ge dimuro nisokare nana osena awa, ata nikare ge naso doro na oko otao inowewa. Noma ema zo kotumai nusora kei nisokare nana nai amire numore dai otao wamunowa.
\v 44 Nikare nitopekare bowi ina-wa inoise nowewa. Ota Anutu imata nikare bowi waise ago kaka samu inowewa ami nogo wero na tuma diamunowi?
\v 45 Nikare namore ego oko sawe, ‘Nune nakai gera potai ge bua wamunonakai.’ Namore ago oko sawe. Nikare Mose tuma diro nowewa, are Mose meni nikare gera potamunoya.
\v 46 Mose meni ge gaenua, awa namore gaenua awa. Nikare ge nuso ninawa me wamia, awa nikare ge naso dai ninawa me wamia.
\v 47 Ota nikare Mosera ge gayai awa niniwa me kaka wamu wenu giro dowa, are nogo nogo wero ge naso ninawa me wamunoi?” Yesu meni ago senua awa.
\c 6
\s1 Yesu meni ema 5,000 amire ma potinu niwa.
\p 
\v 1 Yesu meni ge awa senu tepo wenu Galilaya ou ubu semuro bamu enibara ninua awa. Ou ubu amira zazo zo Taibirias asinowera.
\v 2 Semuro bamunu nu ema bama yayare kora wasai ewanana inoisowa awa eni meni gosinoisowa, are ema diti bamu meni nu ama ganewa awa.
\v 3 Ago wewa Yesu meni bua mai nuso pumuro witi dirumura niro arumuro itiwa awa.
\v 4 Be amira ana Yuda emara pura zo zazo nuso Betai Daininua amira be zora awenua awa.
\v 5 Are Yesu meni ema dubu bamu nuso nana tupiwa giro Filip atata wero ego senua awa, “Ma nana ena puro ema dubu bamu amire potanakai nara te wamunoi?”
\v 6 Yesu nu bua zo wamu kotupitinoinua, ata nu Filip gaero gamu atata wero senua awa.
\v 7 Ago senu Filip meni ego senua awa, “500 kina meni ma pumuro potanakai nara te kaka wamu wamunoi, tanita.”
\v 8 Ago senu bua mai nusora nana zo Anderea, nu Simon Petorora nami, ami ego senua awa,
\v 9 “Mai zo meni ma wana dare ou wo etore puro noya. Ata ema dubu bamu, are te oko wamunoi, tanita.”
\v 10 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Nikare seu ema poti dara niro arumare.” Zebu amira zewaka itisonua, are patiro arumuwa. Namba nusokare 5,000 ago ine ami arumuwa awa.
\p 
\v 11 Ago wewa Yesu meni ma puro Anuture kokopai asero ema arumuro itiwa amire kanowenua. Ou wo da ago ine wenu te wenua.
\v 12 Niwa te wenu itata da ago dowa giro Yesu meni bua mai nusore ego senua awa, “Nena itata itima waya wamera, sianiu.” Ago senua awa.
\v 13 Are ma wana da niwa amira itata awa sianiwa kana 12 ago be muwa.
\v 14 Ema meni tani putoure awa giro Yesu bowi inoise ego sewa awa, “Porofete bamubake zo zebura kei awaise sai awa ewa.”
\v 15 Ago sero Yesu puro ema tua nusokare potara nuaise toiwa giro nu ema dubu awa doro imata witiro bamu dirumura ninua awa.
\s1 Yesu meni ou tame aita wenua.
\p 
\v 16 Tua zinu bua mai nuso meni ou ubura osero
\v 17 Kapaneam nate ewesemuro bayamu sero wara witiro bamuwa awa. Ago susauwa pi zinu Yesu meni nusokare nana kaka kei awamu wenu
\v 18 bisi zewai-zawai munu kakawa bamubake inoinu
\v 19 nukare dawero bamu soe niro 5 kilomita ago awa inoiwa Yesu meni ou tame aita wero baro wa nusokare nana zorage kei awinoinu giro azu wewa awa.
\v 20 Azu wewa giro Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Azu oko wawe. Nane tupena awa.”
\v 21 Ago senu giro nukare yawa sara inoise ziwa wara witinu wa meni nata bayamu sero inoiwa amira eya kei awenua awa.
\s1 Ema bama Yesu tamamu kau wewa.
\p 
\v 22 Pina atinu ema ou ubu enibara awinoiwa ami ego sewa awa, “Pire wa daimata gege iti bua mai nuso meni Yesu doro nukare imata wara witiro bamitara awa.”
\v 23 Ago sewa, ata wa eni Taibirias nate ena muro kakamo Tua meni ma gawa wenu niwa amira muwa awa.
\v 24 Are ema bama meni Yesu bua mai nusore awa kau inomite nukare tamamu sero wa muro itiwa amira witiro bamu Kapaneam nate niwa awa.
\p 
\v 25 Bamu ou enibara niro Yesu kau inomite tamuro ego sewa awa, “Gipai ema, ni nazi mesi?”
\v 26 Ago atata wewa Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Na me memeka sana niniu. Tani putoure wawena gosinowewa amira kota, ma potena nitawa amira gege na kau inowa.
\v 27 Nikare ma sisai amira kota, nuai me ewananara ma amira bua wewo. Na Emara Mai awa Anutu Mama meni putou namore potinu pumuna. Are nuai me ewananara ma awa nane nimorekare potamunona.”
\v 28 Ago senu nukare ge ina ego sewa awa, “Nakare nogo nogo wero Anutura bua wamunonikare?”
\v 29 Ago sewa nu ego senua awa, “Anutura bua ego ewa. Na Anutu meni senu osena, nama awa tuma diwo.”
\v 30 Ago senu nukare ge ina ego sewa awa, “Ni tani putoure ne wasa ganakare ge niso me wamunoi?
\v 31 Ewowo-kawowo nasokare ware noise ma zazo mana awa ninoise noisowa. Amira ge gayai ego itia ewa, ‘Utura ma potasai ninoisowa.’”
\s1 Utura ma amira ge.
\p 
\v 32 Ago sewa Yesu meni numorekare ego senua awa, “Na me memeka sana niniu. Mose meni utura ma nimorekare oko potinua. Mama naso meni utura ma me nimorekare potitinowia awa.
\v 33 Ma Anutu meni potitinowia ami utura ena osero zebura ema nimorekare nuai tapinowia.”
\v 34 Ago senu ina ego sewa awa, “O Tua, ni ma tosa awa be giti namorekare potitinoiyo.”
\v 35 Ago sewa ina ego senua awa, “Nuai potaira ma na ewa. Zo nu namore dara tairo nuamunoya ami meri oko wamunoya. Ota zo nu na tuma diamunoya ami ou uza oko wamunoya.
\p 
\v 36 Na sesena gewa. Nikare na gosinowewa, ata nikare na kaka tuma diamu inowewa.
\v 37 Ema Mama meni namore potitinowia ami dapikarago naso nana kei awamunora. Are zo nu naso nana mai na nu oko esenamunona.
\v 38 Utura ena osena awa kotumai nasora kota, Mamera bera bua nuso wamu sero osena awa.
\v 39 Nu senu osena amira ara tamai ego ewa. Ema dubu namore potinua nukare ami sisero waya wai azu, na be bamura ena awa-uzana dapikarago erarise.
\v 40 Mama nasora ara tamai awa ego ine itia awa. Nukare na Mai giro baitiro tuma diamunora ami nuai me ewanana pumamunora. Ago wara nane be bamura ena nukare awa-uzana eramunora. Mama nasora ara tamai ago itia awa.” Ago senua awa.
\s1 Yesu nu nuai me ewanana amira ma.
\p 
\v 41 Yesu meni, “Ma utura ena osenua na awa,” ago senua, are Yuda ema giwa waya wenu giro ego sewa awa,
\v 42 “Ema awa nu Yesu. Nu Yosefera mai awa. Nakai mia mama nuso gosinowenakai. Are nogoro nu utura ena osenu sia toi?”
\v 43 Ago sewa Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Nikare gung-ga oko sawe.
\v 44 Zo nu kotumai nusora naso nana mai ine oko itia. Mama na senu osena ami nu zumamunoya, awa nu naso nana mamunoya. Ago wai nane be bamura ena awa-uzana seka wero eramunoya.
\v 45 Porofete meni ge zo ego gaewa itewia ewa, ‘Anutu nu nutope ema dapikarago ge nuso tugata wamunoya.’ Are zo nu Mama meni ge gipai niniro kotumai tamamunoya ami naso nana mamunoya.
\v 46 Ema agai meni Mama ginu? Tepo awa. Anutura nana ena osena na daimata ami Mama gina awa.
\v 47 Na me memeka sana niniu. Zo nu na tuma didinoise nowia ami nuai me ewanana awa puro nowia awa.
\v 48 Nuaira ma na ewa.
\v 49 Ewowo-kawowo nisokare ware noise ma zazo mana ninoise bebeteniwa.
\v 50 Ota utura ma niro kaka betamu nuai gege nuai awa na ewa.
\v 51 Nuaira ma utura ena osena na ewa. Are zo nu ma awa namunoya ami nuai gege nuamunoya. Pisi naso meni ma inoya awa. Are erama meni nuai tamarise potamunona.”
\p 
\v 52 Ago senu Yuda ema nutopekare ina-sa wero ego sewa awa, “Nu nogo wero pisi nuso potai nanisekai toi?”
\v 53 Ago sewa Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Na me tona. Nikare Mamera Mai amira pisire orarare kaka namu wamunowa, awa nuai me duba nisokarera oko itamunoya.
\v 54 Zo nu pisi nasore orara nasore namunoya ami nuai me ewanana tamamunoya. Ago wai nane be bamura ena nu awa-uzamunona awa.
\v 55 Pisi naso meni ma me. Orara naso meni ou nai me.
\v 56 Pisi nasore orara nasore namunoya ami namore dai nuamunoya. Ago wai na da ago numore dai nuamunona.
\v 57 Mama nu nuaira Mama ami na senu osena, are nuai na Mamera nana zewai-zawai itawi nowena. Are zo nu na namunoya awa da ago ine nuai nuso naso nana itai nuamunoya.
\v 58 Utura ma amira susu ago itia awa. Awa ewowo-kawowo nisokare meni niwa, ago ine oko aewa. Nukare ma awa ninoise bebeteniwa. Ota zo meni ma ei awa namunoya ami nuai gege nuamunoya.” Ago senua awa.
\v 59 Yesu nu Kapaneam nate ena yere ibura ena ge awa emare tugata wenua awa.
\s1 Eni meni Yesura ge azu sewa.
\p 
\v 60 Dubu nusora nana eni meni ge awa niniro ego sewa awa, “Ge awa ninenakai te kaka wamu inoya. Ge awa agai meni ninai te wamunoi?”
\v 61 Ago toise duba tu meni gung-ga sewa giro Yesu meni enia wero giro ego senua awa, “Ge awa ninewa waya inoita?
\v 62 Are Mamera Mai meni noko ewesemuro utura witana gawa nogo wamunoi?
\v 63 Ozana meni nuai emare potitinowia. Tamara pisi meni oko sorepitinowia. Na ge towena awa Ozanare ata nuaire awa.
\v 64 Ata nikare eni meni niniro na tuma kaka diamu inowewa.” Yesu meni ago senua. Nera kota, nu nukare eni meni ge nuso niniro nu tuma kaka diamu wamunora amira benau nusokare gita ona ginu tepo wenua awa. Ota ema nu kerenamu inoinua amira benau dai ginu tepo wenua. Are ge awa senua awa.
\v 65 Are nu ge zo susumuro ego senua awa, “Na ami emo ego tona awa. Zo nu Mama meni kaka ninamu wai nu naso nana mai ine oko itia.” Ago senua awa.
\v 66 Are be amira ana dubu nuso eni meni numore dai nuai awa biawa wenu giro nu doro bamuwa awa.
\v 67 Ago wewa Yesu meni bua mai nuso 12 atata wero ego senua awa, “Nikare da ago ine na duamu towita?”
\v 68 Ago senu Simon Petoro meni ina ego senua awa, “Tua, ni doro zo ara nana bayamunonikare? Nuai me ewanana amira ge niso nana itewia.
\v 69 Are nakare ni tuma didinoise ego genakare me wetia awa: Ni Anutura Mai saramai.”
\v 70 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na nikare mai 12 sianiro pumuna. Ata nisokare nana zo meni nogoro Satan ine inoi?”
\v 71 Ago senua, awa nu Simon Iskeriot amira mai zazo Yudas amire senua. Nu Yesura bua mai 12 amira otao zo ami ama Yesu kereniro iwora wanera potinua.
\c 7
\s1 Yesura namisini meni nu kaka tuma diamu dowa.
\p 
\v 1 Yesu meni ago senu giro Yuda ema eni meni Yesu damu sero ge diwa dagimunu Yesu meni ge awa niniro giro Yudaya zebu doro Galilaya zebura baro noisonua awa.
\v 2 Ago noinu Yuda emara pura zo zazo Komboara Pura* amira be zora awenua awa.
\v 3 Ago wenu namisini nuso meni numore ego sewa awa, “Ni zebu ei awa doro Yudaya zebura baro bua inowesa awa ona wasa bua mai niso ago nowera ami gare.
\v 4 Ema zo bua inowia ami ema bama garise sero oko bezinowia. Ni bua inowesa, are ni bamuro ema dapikarago amira nana giti mokara kei awero bua awa we gare.” Ago sewa awa.
\v 5 Namisini nuso meni ge ago sewa, nera kota, nukare nu tuma kaka diamu noisowa.
\v 6 Ago sewa Yesu meni numorekare ego senua awa, “Nikare be tepo amira ana bua zo wawewa te inowia. Ata be naso kaka mamu.
\v 7 Ema bama meni nikare iwo wai ine tepo. Ata nane meni awa nuai nusokare waya awa kerenawena giro na iwo inowera.
\v 8 Are nikare aunaira bamuu. Nane aunai amira oko mamunona. Nera kota, be naso kaka kei awamu.”
\v 9 Ago sero nu Galilaya zebura dago itinua awa.
\p 
\v 10 Ago noinu nukare gita bamuwa amire nu ama imata upene bamunua awa.
\v 11 Ago wenu pura zora awenu Yuda ema babezinoma meni nu kau inoise ego sewa awa, “Nu nago iti?” Ago sewa awa.
\v 12 Ota ema dubu bamu ge dainiro sewa. Ago toiwa eni meni ego sewa awa, “Nu ema kokopai.” Ota eni meni ego sewa awa, “Tepowa. Nu opi toise ema bama etete nitinowia.” Ago sewa awa.
\v 13 Ata dubu bamu meni Yuda ema babezinoma awa azu inoise ge tura bezero sewa awa.
\s1 Yesu nu Anutura Oziga Ewanana puro osenua.
\p 
\v 14 Pura soe sieninu Yesu meni Anutura ibu bamu amira mokara toiro ema bama ge tugata wenua.
\v 15 Ge tugata inoinu Yuda ema gita wai meni giro di taniro ego sewa awa, “Nu ninai ibu nasokaira kaka toyamu ami nogo wero ge susure ninitinowi?”
\v 16 Ago sewa Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Na gera susu nimorekare tugata inowena, awa naso kota, na senu osena amira awa.
\v 17 Nikare na kotumai nasora gege towenita Anutura bera ge tugata inoweni, ago towewa. Ata ema zo meni Anutura ge dipinoise nuamunoya ami na ge towena amira susu gamunoya.
\v 18 Zo nu kotumai nusora towia ami tama nuso puro witamu towia. Ata zo nu buara mama amira bowi kei awaise towia ami opi tepo ge me gege towia.
\v 19 Mose meni lo ge nimorekare potinua, ata nisokare nana zo meni oko dipinowia. Nikare nogoro na damu towi?”
\v 20 Ago senu ema bama bamu ami girara asero ego sewa awa, “Ni bi meni duba nisora iti dau wero tosa. Ai meni ni damu toi?”
\v 21 Ago sewa Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na tani putoure daimata wetena nikare di tainiro itewa awa.
\v 22 Sana niniu. Mose meni mai mamatana nisokarera tama aiso agewa kapawise senua. Ota Mose meni kota, ewowo meni zaawewa. Are bua awa waira be mawi pura bera ena inowewa.
\v 23 Awa Mosera sai zewai wai ge dainai azu, nikare pura bera ena mai mamatana nisokarera tama aiso kapinowewa awa. Ota nane meni awa ema zo me zere dago pura be nisokarera ena kora wisena. Amira nikare nogoro namore tini kapai pupinowi?
\v 24 Na pasina wago wisena asero bua naso waya oko sawe. Bua nasora susu giro baitiro amire bua kokota waya ni, awa seu.”
\p 
\v 25 Ge ago senu Yerusalem ema eni meni ego sewa awa, “Ema damu towera awa ewa.
\v 26 Giu. Nu ge damu ena toya, ata nukare numore ge zo kaka samu inora. Pris nukare nu gawera Kristo inowita? Tepo tanita.
\v 27 Nakai kei awai nuso gosinonakai. Ata Kristo mamunoya amira kei awai awa zo meni oko gamunoya.” Ago sewa awa.
\p 
\v 28 Yesu nu Anutura ibu bamura ena dopero ge tugata inoinu ge awa sewa niniro ina ego senua awa, “Nikare na gosinowewa, ota kei awai nasora susu gosinowewa. Ata na kotumai nasora oko osena. Nu senu osena nu awa me awa. Nikare nu oko gosinowewa.
\v 29 Na nuso nana ena osena, noko nune senu osena, are na nu giro baititinowena.” Ago senua awa.
\v 30 Ago senu nukare nu benamu sewa, ata be nuso kaka mamu, are wana nuso nana tame potai awa mou wero dowa awa.
\v 31 Ago wewa ema bama dainiro meni Yesu tuma diro ego sewa awa, “Kristo mamunoya awa ema emi tani putoure inowia awa dainiro wamunoita? Tepo, tanita.” Ago sewa awa.
\p 
\v 32 Ema nukare ge ago ine awa upene toiwa Farisayo meni niniro pris babezinoma enire dai auniro ge sero Yesu benamu ge sero soldia iyetiwa Yesu pamu sero bamuwa awa.
\s1 Yesu nu Mamera nana ewesemamu senua.
\p 
\v 33 Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Na be apunu nimorekare noma nu senu osena amira nana ewesemamunona awa.
\v 34 Ago wana nikare na kau bamubake wero oko tamamunowa. Baro nuamunona amira nikare bayai ine tepo.”
\v 35 Ge ago senu Yuda ema nutopekare ge ina-sa wero ego sewa awa, “Nu nago bayai kau wamunonakai asinoi? Yuda ema otao mamai nasokai Grik zebura nowera amira nana baro Grik ema ge tugata wamu toita?
\v 36 Nu ego sesia, ‘Na kau wero oko tamamunowa. Ota bayamunona amira nikare bayai ine tepo.’ Ge ago ine awa nogo toi?” Ago sewa awa.
\s1 Ama Ozana mamunoya amira ge senua.
\p 
\v 37 Pura be pesunitinoinu Yuda ema meni aunai bamu inoise itiwa amire Yesu meni eriro dopero zawa sero ego senua awa, “Zo nu ou uza wai giro naso nana muro ou naise.
\v 38 Zo nu na tuma diamunoya amira dubara ena nuai me ewanana amira ou sasa ine mai gege tupise itamunoya. Amira ge gayai zo itia awa.” Ago senua awa.
\v 39 Awa ema nu tuma didinora ami Ozana pamunora ago senua. Yesu meni Ozanara ge awa oura potiro ge awa senua. Be amira ana nu utura zasimaira kaka kapeteniro witamu wenua, are Ozana meni kaka osamu wenua.
\p 
\v 40 Ema nukare ge awa niniro ego sewa awa, “Porofete dia inowenakai numa awa.”
\v 41 Ota eni meni ego sewa awa, “Nu Kristo me.” Ago sewa eni meni enira ge dero ego sewa awa, “Kristo meni Galilaya ena nogoro kei awamunoi? Tepo tanita.
\v 42 Anutura ge gayai zo ego ine itia ewa, ‘Kristo nu Dawidira nata susu Betelehem ena saisibuna nusora nana soe ena kei awaise sai.’ Ge gayai ago ine itia.” Ago sewa awa.
\v 43 Ema nukare Yesure ge ago toise zazaumuwa awa.
\v 44 Ago toise eni meni Yesu benamu ge sewa, ata zo da nu oko zinua.
\s1 Yesu benamu ge gege sero dowa.
\p 
\v 45 Soldia nukare pris babezinomare Farisayo nana ewesemuro bamuwa atata wero ego sewa awa, “Nikare nogoro nu kaka puro mamu wetewi?”
\v 46 Ago atata wewa soldia meni ego sewa awa, “Nu ge towia ago ine ema zo meni sai ine oko itia.”
\v 47 Ago sewa Farisayo ema meni ina ego sewa awa, “Nu nukare dai eteteni gewa me wetiwa.
\v 48 Simaire Farisayore nasokare nana zo ai meni nu tuma didinoi?
\v 49 Awa tepo awa. Ata ema dubu bamu nu ama ganinora ami Mosera lo ge kaka gamu inoise nowera, are waru nusokare nana itewia.”
\v 50 Ago sewa otao nusokare zo zazo nuso Nikodemo nu gita be zore Yesura nana bamunua ami ego senua awa,
\v 51 “Nikare seu. Ema zo nakai susu nuso kaka gamu, ota pasina nuso kaka tamamu inoise nu tepo gera potanisekai sai itita? Lo ge nasokai meni go wanisekai toita?”
\v 52 Ago senu otao mamai nuso meni ina ego sewa awa, “Ni da ago Galilaya ema ni? Ni lo ge nasokai azimai bua i-susauma ego gamunosa: Galilaya zebura ena porofete zo kei awaise sai oko itia.” [
\v 53 Ge ago tomite doro so sero bozero bamuwa awa.
\c 8
\s1 Nukare pasina bama zo Yesura nana puro bamuwa.
\p 
\v 1 Yesu nu Oliwa dirumura witinua.
\v 2 Pina atinu ana ewesemuro bamuro Anutura ibu bamura toinu ema dainiro meni nuso nana auniwa giro arumuro ge tugata wenua awa.
\v 3 Ago inoinu lo ge gipai emare Farisayore meni bama zo kuma inoinu tamuwa awa puro poti soe niro Yesure ego sewa awa,
\v 4 “Gipai ema, bama ami bewana inoi tamera.
\v 5 Mose meni lo ge nasokai gainoise bama ego ine awa omata meni danakai betarise senua. Ota ni nitope nogo wanisekare tosi?”
\v 6 Ago sewa, awa ego emira: Nukare nu atata wara ina ge zo sai giro nu puro gera potamu sewa. Ago sewa Yesu nu numorekare ge ina kaka samu. Nu dupuniro zebu owe inoise itinua.
\v 7 Ago wenu nukare nu atata werota wero awewa giro eriro ego senua awa, “Nisokare nana zo meni pasina amu nowia ami omata puro zaawero daise amire dawe.”
\v 8 Ago sero noko dupuniro zebura owe wenua.
\v 9 Ago wenu nukare ge nuso niniro bama awa doro zezewenai meni gita wewa tiri-tara awero baro tepo wewa awa.
\v 10 Ago wewa bama imata itinu Yesu iri niro giro numore ego senua awa, “Nukare nani? Zo meni ni gera potita?”
\v 11 Ago senu bama meni ina ego senua awa, “O Tua, tepo awa.” Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Na da ago ni gera oko potamunona. Ni baro noise pasina noko oko wase.” Ago senua awa.]
\s1 Yesu nu zebura zasimai.
\p 
\v 12 Yesu meni ema bamere ge zo ego senua awa, “Na zebu serora ema amira zasimai. Are zo nu na ama ganamunoya ami mumera oko susawiamunoya. Nu nuaira zasimai nuso nana itai nuamunoya awa.”
\v 13 Ago senu Farisayo ema meni ego sewa awa, “Ni nitope susu niso kerenitinosa, awa genakare me oko inoya.”
\v 14 Ago sewa giro Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na natope susu naso kerenitinona ami me amu oko inoya. Na nana muni, ota nago susaweni, amira susu gosinoise ge towena. Ata ninekare meni awa na nana muni, ota na nago susaweni, amira susu kau inowewa awa.
\v 15 Nikare tama naso gege giro na waya asinowa. Ata nane meni awa erama awina-dawina waira bua oko inona.
\v 16 Ata na awina-dawina waira bua wamena, awa bua me wamia. Nera kota, na imata oko itena. Nu na senu osena ami namore dai nowia awa.
\v 17 Lo ge gayai nisokare amira ego gayai itia awa, ‘Ema eto meni nena zora susu sarato te wamunoya. Ago wai me asamunora.’
\v 18 Are susu naso awa na natope kerenawena Mama na senu osena ami dai kerenitinowia.”
\v 19 Ago senu nukare nu atata wero ego sewa awa, “Mama niso nani?” Ago sewa nu ina ego senua awa, “Nikare na kaka giro baitamu inowewa. Are nikare Mama naso da ago kaka giro baitamu inowewa. Nikare na giro baitamewa, awa Mama naso dai giro baitamewa.” Ago senua awa.
\v 20 Yesu nu ibu bamura itise akou wau moni potitinoisowa amira zorage dopero ge tugata inoise amire ge awa senua. Ota betaira be nuso kaka mamu, are nukare nu kaka ziamu wewa.
\s1 Ema meni awa zebura. Ota Yesu meni awa utura.
\p 
\v 21 Yesu meni numorekare noko ego senua awa, “Na nikare doro bayana na kau wero pasina nisokare amire dai noma betamunowa. Na baro nuamunona amira nikare bayai ine tepo.”
\v 22 Ago senu Yuda ema meni ego ina-sa wewa awa, “Nu ego toya, ‘Na baro nuamunona amira nikare bayai ine tepo.’ Ge ago awa nogo toi? Nu nutope tama dero betamu toita?”
\v 23 Ge ago sewa Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Nikare bagera. Na ikera. Nikare zebura. Na zebura oko aewa.
\v 24 Ami emo na nimorekare ego sesena awa, ‘Nikare pasina nisokare amire dai noma betamunowa.’ Na susu naso kerenitinowena, awa ninawa me kaka wamu wamunoya, awa nikare pasina nisokare amire dai noma betamunowa.”
\v 25 Ago senu nukare noko atata wero ego sewa awa, “Ni aweni?” Ago sewa nu ina ego senua awa, “Na sawena gosinowewa.
\v 26 Na pasina nisokare dainiro kereniro nikare gera potamu wero giro te wero baitamena. Ata nu na senu osena ami ge me towia. Are nane be nusora nana ena ninina da awa gege zebura ena kerenitinowena.” Ago senua awa.
\v 27 Nu Mamere ago senu nukare kaka giro baitamu wewa awa.
\v 28 Are Yesu meni noko ego senua awa, “Nikare na Emara Mai awa ni pasinaira ikoniro amire susu naso gamunowa awa. Be amire na bua inowena awa kotumai nasora oko inowena awa gamunowa. Mama meni gipenua ge awa puro noise towena awa dai gamunowa.
\v 29 Nu na senu osena ami namore dai nowia. Be giti bamu awa bua wawena giro ara tapinowia. Are nu na kaka duwamu nowia.” Ago senua awa.
\s1 Pasinara soumai amira ge.
\p 
\v 30 Yesu ge ago senu ema dainiro meni nu tuma diwa.
\v 31 Nukare awa Yuda ema, are Yesu meni numorekare ego senua awa, “Nikare ge naso niniro baitiro dimuro nuamunowa, awa nikare mai dubu naso me wero nuamunowa.
\v 32 Nikare ago inoise ge me niniro baitawa ami mui nisokare besamunoya. Besai mui amu kokopai nuamunowa awa.”
\v 33 Ago senu ina ego sewa awa, “Nakare Abrahamra saisibuna. Nakare ema zora soumai kaka wamu nowenakare. Nakare mui amu nuamunonakare, awa sesesa amira susu nogo iti?”
\v 34 Ago sewa Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na me memeka sane. Zo nu pasina inowia ami pasinara soumai inoya.
\v 35 Soumai meni ema tua nusora ibu marara oko nuai gege nuamunoya. Ata ema tuara mai meni mamera ibu marara nuai gege nuamunoya awa.
\v 36 Are Mai meni nikare besamunoya, awa nikare mui amu me amu nuamunowa.
\v 37 Nikare Abrahamra saisibuna awa gosinona. Ata ge naso meni nisokare nana mokara kaka toyamu inowia, are nikare na dawa betanise towa.
\v 38 Na Mama nasora nana ena nena gosinoise noisona awa nikare tugata inowena, ata ninekare meni awa mama nisokarera niniwa awa inowewa awa.”
\v 39 Ago senu nukare ina ego sewa awa, “Nakare mama nakare Abraham.” Ago sewa Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Nikare Abrahamra saisibuna nuamewa sia, awa nikare Abrahamra tani puro nuamewa.
\v 40 Anutura nana ena ge me susure ninina awa nikare tugata inowena, nama nogoro damu towi? Goroba ago ine awa Abraham meni oko wenua.
\v 41 Nikare mama nisokarera bua inowewa.” Ago senu nukare ego sewa awa, “Nakare eba mai oko aewa. Anutu nu Mama nasokare daimata.”
\v 42 Ago sewa Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Mama nisokare Anutu sia, awa nikare na ara tamamewa. Nera kota, na Anutura nana ena muro nowena. Na kotumai nasora oko osena. Anutu meni senu osena.
\v 43 Nikare nogoro ge naso kaka gamu inowewi? Nikare kaka gamu inowewa, nera kota, ge towena awa nikare ninai ine tepo.
\v 44 Nikare mama nisokare Satan amira mai awiso, are ara tamai nuso ama ganero bua waya awa wamu towewa. Nu gita ona ema dasai betinoisowa, da ago ine i-tupewia awa. Nu ge me oko puro nowia. Nera kota, ge me zo nuso nana oko itia. Opi ge nuso meni nuso nana mokara be munua, are nu opi saira mama wero nowia awa.
\v 45 Na ge me gege tona, are nikare ge naso gewa me kaka wamu inoya.
\v 46 Nisokare nana zo meni na pasina ema ago sai me wamunoita? Tepo awa. Na ema agami ge me susure tugata wawena nogoro gawewa me kaka wamu inowi?
\v 47 Zo nu Anutura mai wero nowia ami Anutura ge ninitinowia. Nikare Anutura mai oko nowewa, are ge nuso azu towewa awa.” Ago senua awa.
\s1 Abraham kaka kei awamure Yesu noisonua nowia.
\p 
\v 48 Ago senu Yuda ema meni ego sewa awa, “Nakare nimore ego tonakare: Ni Samaria ema. Bi meni niso nana itia. Nimore ago toise ge me tonakare.”
\v 49 Ago sewa Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Bi naso nana mokara oko itia. Na Mama naso bowi inowena, ata ninekare meni awa zazo naso puro osisinowewa.
\v 50 Na zazo bowire naso wamu oko towena. Zo itia ami zazo naso de ike nitinowia. Nune zas inoya.
\v 51 Na me memeka sana niniu. Zo nu ge naso niniro puro nuamunoya ami oko betamunoya. Nu nuai gege nuamunoya.”
\v 52 Ge ago senu Yuda ema nukare ego sewa awa, “Bi niso nana mokara itia awa me towenakare. Abraham betenua, ota porofete eni nukare da ago bebeteniwa. Ata ni ego tosa, ‘Zo nu ge naso puro nuamunoya ami oko betamunoya.’
\v 53 Mama nasokare Abraham betenua. Ota nine nu dainamu tosita? Ina porofete dago betewa awa. Ni nogoro tama niso puro wititinosi?”
\v 54 Ago sewa Yesu meni numorekare ego senua awa, “Na tama naso puro witana te oko wamunoya. Mama naso nowia, awa nikare Anutu nisokare asinowewa, nune ami na bowi inowia.
\v 55 Nikare nu giro kaka giro baitamu inowewa. Nane meni awa giro baititinowena awa. ‘Na nu kaka gamu inowena,’ ago samena, awa na opi sai ema nikare ine wamena. Na nu giro baititinoise ge nuso dipinoise nowena awa.
\v 56 Mama nisokare Abraham nu kei awaira be naso gamu sero yawa sara inoise noisonua. Are nu be naso giro yawa sara wenua awa.”
\v 57 Ago senu Yuda ema meni ina ego sewa awa, “Ni zepa niso 50 kaka wamu ami Abraham gisita?”
\v 58 Ago sewa nu ego senua awa, “Na me memeka sane. Na Abraham kaka kei awamure noisona nowena ewa.”
\v 59 Ago senu nukare omata puro damu sero wewa ibu mokara ena tara awero kei awenua awa.
\c 9
\s1 Yesu meni ema giti guma wai zo kora wenua.
\p 
\v 1 Yesu nu susaumite ema zo miera nana tinira ena giti guma wai kei awero itisonua awa tamunua.
\v 2 Ago wenu bua mai nuso meni nu atata wero ego sewa awa, “Gipai ema, pasina ara amira ema ei awa giti guma wenu? Pasina nuso amirata mia mamera amira ni?”
\v 3 Ago sewa Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Amira oko aewa. Pasina nusorata mia mamera amira oko aewa. Anutu putou nusora susu ami ema emira nana kei awaise ago wenua awa.
\v 4 Ema bama waikore bua wawera pi ziawi giro bua dotinowera, da ago ine nakai nama senu osena amira bua waikore inoise nuanekai. Be zo mai amire bua nuso waira be tepo wamunoya.
\v 5 Na zebura nuamunona, te zasimai naso meni nikare zasipitinuamunoya awa.”
\v 6 Ago sero pora we zebura niro zebure dawero puro emara gitira anenua awa.
\v 7 Anero iyetitinoise ego senua awa, “Ni baro Siloam ou butura ana benau niso sewe.” Ago senua awa. (Siloam awa ge nasokaira “Iyetai”). Are ema awa baro ou butu amira ana giti moka sewenu giti moka keenua awa.
\v 8 Giti moka keenu ewesemunu otao mamaita ema nu nena emo begomo tuasai gosinoisowa ami nu giro ego sewa awa, “Nena emo begomo toise itewia awa ni, tanita?”
\v 9 Ago sewa eni meni ego sewa awa, “Nu awa.” Ota eni meni ego sewa awa, “Nu tepo, ata nu ine zo.” Ago toiwa nu nutope ego senua awa, “Zo tepo, ata na ewa.”
\v 10 Ago senu nukare nu atata wero ego sewa awa, “Nogo nogo wetesa giti moka niso kokopai weti?” Ago sewa nu ego senua awa,
\v 11 “Ema zo zazo nuso Yesu ami zebu dawero giti moka nasora anero ego sero iyetia awa, ‘Siloam ou butura baro benau niso sewe.’ Ago sesi baro sewetena giti moka naso keetia.”
\v 12 Ago senu nukare atata wero ego sewa awa, “Ema awa nago noi?” Ago sewa nu ego senua awa, “Na kaka gamu inona.” Ago senua awa.
\s1 Farisayo nukare ema giti guma wai amira ge sewa.
\p 
\v 13 Ago senu nukare ema gita nu giti guma wai awa puro bamu Farisayo dubura nana niwa.
\v 14 Yesu meni zebu dawero emara giti mokara anenu keenua, awa Sabat pura amire wenua.
\v 15 Are Farisayo nukare da ago atata wero ego sewa awa, “Ni nogo wetesa giti moka niso keeti?” Ago sewa ema giti guma wai ami ego senua awa, “Nu zebu dawero giti moka nasora aneti na baro oura ena sewetena giti moka keetia.”
\v 16 Ago senu Farisayo eni meni ego sewa awa, “Ema awa Sabat purara ge sai zewai wai awa doinoya, are nu Anutura nana ena oko munua.” Ota nusokare nana eni meni ego sewa awa, “Nu ema waya nuami sia, awa tani putoure ago ine oko wamia.” Ago toise ge ina-sa wero zazaumuwa awa.
\v 17 Ago tomite ema giti guma wai awa noko atata wero ego sewa awa, “Giti niso sesi keetia numore nogo tosi?” Ago sewa nu ego senua awa, “Nu porofete.”
\v 18 Ago senu Yuda ema meni ema giti keenua amira ge niniro giro, “Gita nu giti guma wai tepota,” asero mia mama nuso zawa sewa muwato atata wero ego sewa awa,
\v 19 “Ei awa mai nisoto ni? Nu giti guma wai tinira ena kei awenuta? Ota nu nogoro giti moka keeti?”
\v 20 Ago atata wewa ina ego sewato awa, “Nu mai nasoto awa gosinonato. Ota nu giti guma wai tinira ena kei awenua, awa gosinonato.
\v 21 Ata nogo wero giti moka keeti amira susu nato kaka gamu inonato. Ata ai meni giti nuso sesi kokopai weti, awa nato kaka gamu inonato. Nu baziro ema wai, are nikare nu atata weu sai gawe.”
\v 22 Mia mama nuso meni Yuda ema azu weroto ge ago sewato. Nera kota, Yuda ema nukare ge emoko ego sewa zewai wenua awa, “Zo nu Yesure ‘Nu Kristo’ asamunoya, nu awa tunero yere ibura ena esenamunonakai awa.”
\v 23 Ago sewa, are mia mama nuto azu wero ego sewato awa, “Nu baziro ema wai, are nikare nu atata weu sai gawe.”
\p 
\v 24 Are nukare ema giti guma wai awa noko zawa sewa munu ego sewa awa, “Ni Anutura benaura ena ge me se. Nakare ema amira susu gosinonakare. Nu ema waya.”
\v 25 Ago sewa nu ina ego senua awa, “Nu ema wayata nogo wai ni, awa na kaka gamu inona. Ata na giti guma wai noe dotena giti moka keetia ami meni awa gosinona.”
\v 26 Ago senu nukare noko atata wero ego sewa awa, “Nimore nogo nogo weti, o nogo wero weti giti moka niso keeti?”
\v 27 Ago sewa nu ina ego senua awa, “Na aware sesena awa. Nikare nogoro kaka ninamu wetewi? Nogoro sai matu da awa noko sana ninamu towi? Nikare dai bua mai nuso wamu towita?”
\v 28 Ago senu nukare nu gona inoise ego sewa awa, “Nine bua mai nuso zo wero nosa. Nanekare meni awa Mosera bua mai awa.
\v 29 Anutu meni Mosere ge tugata wenua. Ami meni awa ninitinowenakare. Ata ema awa nana ena kei awero munu, ami meni awa nakare kaka gamu inonakare.”
\v 30 Ago sewa ema giti moka keenua ami di tainiro ego senua awa, “Nikare kei awai nusora susu kaka gamu inowa, ata saineba, nu weti giti naso keetia awa.
\v 31 Nakai ego ine ninitinowenakai: Anutu meni ema waya-kawaya amira isa sai oko ninitinoya. Ata zo nu Anutu bowi inoise Anutura ara tamai inoya amira isa sai awa Anutu meni ninamunoya.
\v 32 Ota ema zo giti guma wai tinira ena kei awenu zo senu giti keenua amira uge zo oko itia. Nakai uge zo ago ine gita ona kaka ninamu tupise noisonakai nowenakai.
\v 33 Are ema awa Anutura nana ena kaka mamu wami sia, awa nu bua ago ine wai ine te oko wamia.”
\v 34 Ago senu nukare ego sewa awa, “Ni tinira ena kei awero pasina mai nowesa ami nakare tugata wamu tosita?” Ago sero nu yere ibura ena musuniro eseniwa awa.
\s1 Dubara giti guma wai amira ge.
\p 
\v 35 Eseniwa Yesu meni niniro nu tamuro ego senua awa, “Nine Emara Mai tuma didinosita?” Ago senu nu ina ego senua awa,
\v 36 “O Tua, ni are tosi? Gipe giro tuma diane.”
\v 37 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Ni nu goitasa awa. Na ge tona, na ewa.”
\v 38 Ago senu ema giti guma wai ami ego senua awa, “O Tua, na ni tuma didinona.” Ago sero muro nuso nana te gitira ena koininua awa.
\v 39 Ago wenu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Na ema susu nisokare kerenamu sero zebura osena awa. Ema duba giti guma wai ami garise sero, ota ema ‘nakare gai’ asinowera ami duba giti guma wai itarise sero osena awa.”
\v 40 Ago senu Farisayo eni numore dai dopero itiwa ami niniro ego sewa awa, “Nakare dai duba giti guma wai ni?”
\v 41 Ago sewa Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Nikare duba giti guma wai nuamewa sia, awa pasinara ina nisokare nana oko itamia. Ata nitopekare ego towewa, ‘Nakare gai awa.’ Are pasinara ina nisokare nana itai gege itewia.” Ago senua awa.
\c 10
\s1 Lama dubu meni diara ge ninitinowera.
\p 
\v 1 Yesu meni ge ego senua awa, “Na me memeka sana niniu. Zo nu lamara goma amira toyamu sero so be doro demese ena goma zausemuro bamu mokara nitinoya, nu awa bewana ema. Nu nena ewera pai ema.
\v 2 Zo nu so be piakaniro toitinoya, nu ami lama dia me awa.
\v 3 Nu mawi giro so be dia wai meni so be piakanawi lama nuka nuso meni ge bapu nuso ninawera goma mokara ena zazo nusokare sero sero awero uzumuro puro susawewia awa.
\v 4 Nu lama nuso uzumawi ge bapu nuso ninawera nu gita wawi nukare nu ama ganero susawewera.
\v 5 Ota ema zo ewe awa nukare oko ama anamunora. Nukare ge bapu nuso ewe niniro azu wero sumamunora.”
\v 6 Yesu nu ge bezai awa senu nukare ge nusora susu kaka gamu wewa.
\s1 Yesu nu lamara so be.
\p 
\v 7 Yesu meni noko sero senua awa, “Na me memeka sana niniu. Lama toitinowera amira so be awa na ewa.
\v 8 Na kaka kei awamure gita kei awewa nukare awa bewana ema. Nukare nena ewera pai ema. Ata lama meni ge nusokare doro azu wewa awa.
\v 9 Lamara so be awa na ewa. Zo nu goma mokara toyamu sero naso nana mamunoya, awa nu Anutu meni soero pamunoya. Ago wai nu toiro pusumuro awinoise nena zamai bamubake tamamunoya.
\v 10 Bewana ema nu lama bewana wamu sero, o damu sero, o dero tepo-tapo wamu sero tupewia. Ata nane meni awa lama zamai bamubakere kokopai nuarise sero kei awena awa.
\p 
\v 11 Na lama dia wai kokopai. Dia kokopai meni lama dubu emo nuai nuso duamunoya.
\v 12 Ota soumai meni awa, nu dia me tepo. Lama awa nuso kota, ewera, are abu suna kei awai giro nu lama dubu doro azu bayai abu suna meni gamai bozamunora.
\v 13 Nu soumai gege. Nu lama dubu emo oko kotupitinoya. Are nu doro susawia.
\v 14-15 Na dia kokopai nowena. Nato Mamere ina-ga inowenato, da ago ine na ata lama dubu naso nakare ina-ga inoise nowenakare. Are na lama dubu emo nuai naso dotinona awa.
\v 16 Lama dubu naso zo nora, awa nukare goma emira oko aewa. Are na baro uzumuro puro mana ge naso ninamunora. Ago wana lama dubu daimata wero dia daimata wero nuamunora.
\v 17 Na nuai naso doro noko pamunona, are Mama meni na ara tapinowia.
\v 18 Nuai naso awa ema zo meni oko soero pamunoya. Awa kotumai nasora duamunona. Na nuai naso doro noko pamunona amira putou na itia. Mama naso meni ago wanise senua awa.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 19 Yuda ema nukare ge awa niniro zaumuro dubu eto wewa.
\v 20 Dubu bamu meni ego sewa awa, “Bi meni mokara toi dau inoya. Nogoro ge nuso ninitinowi?”
\v 21 Ata eni meni ego sewa awa, “Bire meni ge ago ine oko samunoya. Bi meni ema giti guma wewenai awa sai giti panamunorita? Tepo awa.” Ago sewa awa.
\s1 Yesura wanera ena lama dubu nuso soero pai ine oko itia.
\p 
\v 22 Yuda emara pura zo zazo nuso Ibu Bamu Korawewa* amira be munu giro nukare Yerusalem ena auniwa. Be awa zazamara be.
\v 23 Are Yesu meni ibu bamura osi zo zazo nuso Solomonra Osi amira izima-sauma awinoinu
\v 24 Yuda ema nukare nu zimuro atata wero ego sewa awa, “Ni nogoro susu niso bezawesa nakare itazaita inowenikare? Ni Soyai Ema nasokare Kristo me noma giro kereniro se ganekare.”
\v 25 Ago sewa Yesu meni numorekare ina ego senua awa, “Na sesena ninisewa, ata ninewa me kaka wamu inoya. Ata bua eni na Mama nasora bera inowena ami susu naso kerenitinowia.
\v 26 Ata nikare lama dubu nasoko, are ge naso ninewa me kaka wamu inoya.
\v 27 Lama dubu naso wero nowera nukare awa ge naso ninitinowera. Are nane nukare gosinuawena na ama ganinowera.
\v 28 Ago wawera na nuai me ewanana numorekare potawena kaka betamu nuai gege nowera. Nukare wana nasora ena zo meni soero pai ine oko itia.
\v 29 Mama naso meni nukare namore potinua awa. Mama naso meni ema dapikarago ata nena dapikarago awa dainitinowia. Are zo meni Mama nasora wanera ena nukare soero pai ine tepo.
\v 30 Na ata Mama awa nato daimata.” Ago senua awa.
\s1 Yesu meni Yuda emare bua nusora ge senua.
\p 
\v 31 Ago senu Yuda ema nukare omata meni Yesu noko damu wewa.
\v 32 Damu inoiwa Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Bua kokopai dainiro Mamera soremai amira wetena gewa, are nikare tani na-awa giro na omata meni damu towi?”
\v 33 Ago senu nukare be nusora puro ego sewa awa, “Bua kokopai inowesa amira kota, ni da ago ema nowesa ami Anutu dainitinoise ni nitope Anutu asinowesa, ami emo nakare ni omata meni damu tonakare.”
\v 34 Ago sewa Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Lo ge nisokarera ego gayai itia awa, ‘Anutu meni ego senua awa: Nikare tua.’
\v 35 Agoro ge gayai itia awa doro zo sai ine oko itia. Are Anutura ge ewowo-kawowo nasokai amira nana kei awenu giro nu nukare ‘Tua’ asenua,
\v 36 noko Mama nama gita ose zebura nanise sero na senu osena. Are na natope Anutura Mai asawena nikare nogoro na Anutu dainamu inona asinowewi?
\v 37 Bua inowena awa gawa Mama nasora ine kaka wamu wamunoya, awa ge naso duawa te wamunoya.
\v 38 Ota gawa Mama nasora ine wamunoya, awa ge nasora kota, bua wai nasora na gawa me waise. Ago inoise Mama meni namore dai nowia, da ago ine na Mamere dai nowena, amira susu awa giro baitamunowa.”
\v 39 Ago senu giro nukare nu benamu sero wewa doro bamunua awa.
\p 
\v 40 Yesu nu baro ou Yodan enibara Yohane meni gita ema bama ge ou gutinoisonua ago baro noisonua awa.
\v 41 Ago noinu ema dainiro meni nuso nana baro ego sewa awa, “Yohane nu tani putoure zo kaka wamu. Ata ge Yohane meni ema emire sisia awa me inoya.”
\v 42 Are ema dainiro meni so amira ana Yesu tuma diwa awa.
\c 11
\s1 Lasaro betenua.
\p 
\v 1 Betani natara ema zo noisonua zazo nuso Lasaro. Nu ami yaya puro itinua. Mariato Matare, nuto maeto zawere, nuto nata da amira.
\v 2 (Maria ou zamare meni Tuara te sewero giti tu nuso meni Tuara te gaenua amira numata Lasaro ami yaya puro itinua.)
\v 3 Are maeto zawere meni Yesura nana ge ego ine potiwato bamunua, “O Tua, ni nini. Otao niso yaya puro itia.”
\v 4 Ge ago potiwato bamunu Yesu meni niniro giro ego senua awa, “Yaya amira me awa betai kei awaise kota, ema bama meni Anutu bowi warise sai awa. Ema bama meni Anutura Mai bowi warise sero yaya awa kei awitaya.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 5 Yesura ara tamai awa Matato zawere ata Lasaro amira nana itisonua.
\v 6 Are nu yaya ge niniro waiko be eto dago itinua.
\v 7 Ago itimite nusokare nana bayamu sero bua mai nusore ego senua awa, “Muu. Yudaya zebura ewesemuro bayanekai.”
\v 8 Ago senu bua mai nuso meni ego sewa awa, “Gipai ema, waiko be zo omire Yuda ema omata meni ni damu sisera, awa nogoro amire noko nusokare nana ewesemanisekai tosi?”
\v 9 Ago sewa Yesu meni bua waira be nuso kaka tepo wamu dago itinua awa garise sero ge bezai zo ego senua awa, “Bua waira be 12 aua itia awa. Zo nu waikore ebete susauma te oko koinamunoya. Nera kota, nu zebura zasimai gosinoya.
\v 10 Zo nu pire ebete zasimai tepo susauma te koiniro duwamunoya.”
\v 11 Ago sero ge zo ego senua awa, “Otao nasokai Lasaro gitawa inoya, ata nakai barokai na nu awa-uzamunona.”
\v 12 Ago senu bua mai nuso meni ego sewa awa, “Tua, nu auro kokopai wamunoya.”
\v 13 Yesu meni betaira ge awa gitawa waira potiro senu bua mai nuso meni gitawa mere toita asero ago sewa awa.
\v 14 Are Yesu meni kereniro ego senua awa, “Lasaro betitaya.
\v 15 Na ago kaka baro nuamu ego nona betitaya, are na nikare emo duba naso kokopai inoya. Nikare tuma diai mere nuawise nena awa kei awitaya. Are nuso nana bayanekai.”
\v 16 Ago senu Tomas zazo nuso zo Didimo nune ami otao mamaire ego senua awa, “Nakai baro numore dai betanekai.” Ago senua awa.
\s1 Yesu nu seka wero erai ata nuai amira mama.
\p 
\v 17 Lasaro bi ditira itinu be zoeto-zoeto wenu amire Yesu baro kei awenua.
\v 18 Betani nata awa Yerusalem nana zorage kena itinua. Bayaira ebata awa kilomita 4 gege.
\v 19 Are Yuda ema dainiro meni Matato Mariara numata betenua awa gamu muwa awa.
\v 20 Are Mata nu “Yesu tupia,” ago sewa giro Maria sora dago itinu nune baro Yesu ebete ena tamunua.
\v 21 Tamuro numore ego senua awa, “O Tua, ni ego nuamesa, awa numata naso oko betamia.
\v 22 Agoro na susu niso gosinona. Ni zeme nena zo emo Anutu isa sasa ninamunoya.”
\v 23 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Numata niso seka wero eramunoya.”
\v 24 Ago senu Mata meni ina ego senua awa, “Ama be bamura ena seka wero eramunoya awa gosinona.”
\v 25 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Seka wero erai ata nuai amira mama na ewa. Are zo nu na tuma diamunoya ami betero noko eriro nuamunoya.
\v 26 Ota zo nu seka noise na tuma diro nuamunoya ami kaka betamu seka nuai gege nuamunoya. Ni ge awa ninesa me inoita?”
\v 27 Ago senu Mata meni ego senua awa, “Ni Kristo, Anutura Mai me. Ni zebura osasise sai, awa ninena me weti giro ni tuma didinona.”
\p 
\v 28 Ago sero baro zawa nuso Maria zawa senu munu upene ego senua awa, “Gipai ema muro ni zawa toya.”
\v 29 Ago senu Maria meni niniro eya eriro Yesura nana bamunua.
\v 30 Yesu nu nata atura ena Matare ge senua zara da amira dopero itinua.
\v 31 Itinu Maria eriro bamunu Yuda ema betaira muro itiwa ami “Maria bi ditira ena di samu susawia,” asero ama ganero bamuwa.
\v 32 Are Maria nu ose nata atura niro Yesu tamuro nuso nana koiniro ego senua awa, “O Tua, ni ego nuamesa, awa numata naso oko betamia.”
\v 33 Ago sero di senu Yuda ema Maria ama ganewa ami Maria giro da ago di eroma sewa awa. Di sewa Yesu meni ginu mou wenu koininua awa.
\s1 Yesu meni Lasaro awa-uzenu seka wero erinua.
\p 
\v 34 Yesu meni atata wero ego senua awa, “Nu nago gowitawi?” Ago atata wenu ego sewa awa, “Tua, mu gase.”
\v 35 Ago sewa Yesu di senu diriu munua.
\v 36 Ago wenu Yuda ema nukare nu giro ego sewa awa, “Giu. Duba nuso bamubake Lasaro nana itia.”
\v 37 Ago sewa eni meni ego sewa awa, “Giti guma wai zo senu giti panenua da ago ine ema ei awa betai azu wero nu kora wai kokopai wai te kaka wamu inoita?”
\v 38 Ago toiwa Yesu ge awa niniro moka nuso meni yaya bamubake tamuro bamu bi ditira ninua. Betaira masi awa omata bamubake meni dereweniwa baro be gazenua.
\v 39 Are Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Omata be gazai awa derewieu bayae.” Ago senu Mata nu betaira nubama ami ego senua awa, “Tua, nu waiko zoeto-zoeto awia, are gugumu toya.”
\v 40 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na ego sesena awa, ‘Ni na tuma diamunosa, awa ni Anutura putou gamunosa.’ Ge awa sesena ninesita?”
\v 41 Ago senu omata dereweniwa bamunu Yesu meni iri ike niro ego senua awa, “Mama, ni isa naso nenesa, are na nimore kokopai asinona.
\v 42 Ni isa naso be giti ninitinowesa awa gosinowena. Ata ema dubu emi nine sesa osena awa gara me waise sero ge ago tona awa.”
\v 43 Ago sero zawa sero ego senua awa, “Lasaro, ni pusumuro mu.”
\v 44 Zawa senu betai meni pusumuro munua awa. Te-wana nuso mo meni dowai, ota benau nuso mo meni gopai, are Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Mo beseu bayae.” Ago senu mo besewa bamunua awa.
\s1 Yesu betaise sewa.
\p 
\v 45 Yuda ema Maria nana muro itiwa amira nana dainiro meni tani putoure awa giro Yesu tuma diwa awa.
\v 46 Ata eni meni awa Farisayo emara nana bamuro Yesu meni tani wenua amira ge uge wewa awa.
\v 47 Are pris babezinomare Farisayo ema nukare ge awa niniro giti kopi dubu zawa sewa muwa auniro ego sewa awa, “Ema ami tani putoure dainiro inowia, are nu nogo wamunonikai?
\v 48 Nakai nu duanakai tani ago ine inuai ema dapikarago nu tuma diara Roma emara soldia meni nakai iwo wero muro ibu bamu nasokaire dubu nasokaire awa gera wamunora.”
\v 49 Ago sewa otao nusokare zo zazo Kayafa nu zepa amire pris bamu wero noisonua ami ego senua awa, “Nikare kotumai tepo nowewa.
\v 50 Nikare ego giu. Ebata kokopai ego itia awa. Ema dubu nakai waya wai azu, ema daimata ami nakai emo betaise.” Ago senua awa.
\v 51 Ge awa kotumai nusora oko senua. Nu zepa be amire pris bamu wero noisonua, are nu porofete meni sago wero Yesu nu Yuda ema dubu emo betamu inoinua amira ge senua.
\v 52 Yesu betamu inoinua, awa Yuda ema emo gege kota, nu Anutura mai awiso zebu sero nowera nukare dapikarago poti dara nai dubu daimata wero nuarise betamu inoinua awa.
\v 53 Are giti kopi dubu nukare waiko be amire Yesu puro daira ge bua zaawewa.
\v 54 Are Yesu nu Yuda emara nana noko kaka kei awero nuamu. Nu bua mai nuso puro bamuro nata zo zazo Efraim ware kena itinua amira noisowa awa.
\p 
\v 55 Yuda emara pura zo zazo Betai Daininua amira be zora awenu giro nata pei-mamaira ema dainiro meni pasina disaira buara gita witiro bamu Yerusalem niwa.
\v 56 Are nukare Yesu kau inoise ibu bamura auniro ina-sa wero ego sewa awa, “Nikare nogo towi? Nu pura emire mamunoita, tepo ni?”
\v 57 Pris babezinomare Farisayo emare nukare sai zewai wai ge ego sewa awa, “Ema zo meni nu tamuro giro saise nu puro benare.” Ago sewa awa.
\c 12
\s1 Maria nu Yesu ou zamare meni gutenua.
\p 
\v 1 Betai Daininua amira pura nusokarera waiko be 6 ago itinu Yesu meni Betani nate kei awenua. Nu gita nata amira ana Lasaro betaira ena awa-uzenu seka wero erinua awa.
\v 2 Are Yesu emo nena sawewa Mata meni dumunu Lasaro dai arumuro nena niwa awa.
\v 3 Nena ninoise itiwa Maria meni boto kiaka zo ou zamare kokopai zazo nuso nad zuma bamubakere, awa puro Yesura te gutero giti tu nuso meni te nuso gaenua awa. Ago wenu so itiwa awa zama sere-sere wenua awa.
\v 4 Ago wenu Yudas Iskeriot, nu Yesu kerenamu noinua, ami ego senua awa,
\v 5 “Nakai nogoro ou zamare awa potanakai 300 kina meni zuma gaero pumara moni awa bogamasare kaka potamu wetenikai?”
\v 6 Nu ema bogamasare kotumuro oko senua. Yesu bua maire amira moni awa kaita zora potasara Yudas meni dia inoise moni eni bewana pupinoisonua awa. Are ge awa senua awa.
\v 7 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Nikare bamere ge oko sawe. Nu ou zamare awa puro nuai na betana amire woi naso gutai gowawe.
\v 8 Erama bogamasa nukare be giti nimorekare dai nowera nuamunora. Ata nane meni awa nimorekare dai oko nuai gege nuamunona.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 9 Yesu nata amira noinua amira oziga Yuda ema dainiro meni niniro muwa. Ota nukare Yesu gege gamu kota, Lasaro betaira ena awa-uzenu seka wero erinua awa dai gamu muwa.
\v 10 Are pris babezinoma meni Lasaro dai damu ge bua wewa awa.
\v 11 Nera kota, Yuda ema dainiro meni Lasaro awa-uzenu seka wero erinua awa giro pris babezinoma doro Yesu tuma diwa, are nukare Lasaro dai damu sewa awa.
\s1 Yesu nu Yerusalem witinu ema bama meni yawa sara wewa.
\p 
\v 12 Pina atinu ema dubu bamubake meni pura nusokarera Yerusalem auniwa ami ge oziga ego niniwa awa, “Yesu tupia.”
\v 13 Ge awa niniro giro ni gomi bozero wane-wane wero ebete ena tamamu bamuwa awa. Tamuro yawa sara inoise ego sewa awa, “Tuara bera nasokai nana tupia, nu awa bowi wanekai. Nu Tua nasokai Isreli emara.”
\v 14 Yesu nu wo donki mai zo tamuro amira tame witiro arumuro bamunua. Awa ge gayai ego itia amira te wenua awa:
\li1 
\v 15 Zion natara, nikare azu oko wawe.
\li2 Giu. Ema tua nisokare tupia.
\li2 Nu wo donki maira tame arumuro tupia.
\v 16 Ge awa gita bua mai nuso meni kaka giro baitamu wewa awa. Noe Yesu nu witi utu zasimai nusora ninu amire ge awa kotumuro susu giwa awa. Ge awa numore gayai, are amira te wewa awa.
\p 
\v 17 Nukare dubu bamu meni Yesu Lasaro zawa senu bi ditira ena kei awenu giwa ami ge uge wewa dubu bamu meni niniwa.
\v 18 Tani amira oziga niniwa, are ema dainiro meni baro nu ebete ena tamuwa awa.
\v 19 Ago wewa Farisayo nukare nutopekare ego toise sewa awa, “Gosinowa. Nikare ge bua gege kaputitinowa. Ema dapikarago nuso nana gege susawera.” Ago sewa awa.
\s1 Grik ema eni meni Yesu gamu sewa.
\p 
\v 20 Yuda ema pura nusokarera Yerusalem aunitinoiwa Grik ema eni meni numorekare dai aunai amira noiwa awa.
\v 21 Are Grik ema ami Filip, nu Besaida natara Galilaya zebura, amira nana baro ego sewa awa, “Otao, nakare Yesu gamu tonakare.”
\v 22 Ago sewa Filip meni baro Anderea sero eroma Yesura nana baro sewato awa.
\v 23 Sewato Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na Emara Mai meni simai zasimaire pumamunona, amira be zora awinoya.
\v 24 Na ge me memeka sana niniu. Koni me zo zebura duro kaka zasamu wamunoya, awa nu imata tepo itamunoya. Ata nu zebura duro zasero eramunoya, awa nu me witai ziamunoya.
\v 25 Da ago ine, zo nu nuai nuso ara tapinowia amira nuai tepo wamunoya awa. Zo nu zebura noise nuai nuso iwo inowia ami nuai nuso zizinoise nuai me ewanana tamamunoya awa.
\v 26 Zo nu soumai naso wero nuamu wero giro na ama waise. Ago wero na nuamunona amira soumai naso nuamunoya awa. Zo nu na sou wamunoya nu awa Mama naso meni simamunoya.
\p 
\v 27 Zeme moka naso meni mamana awero zipinoya. Are na nogo samunoni? Mama, ni yaya ei awa musuni. Ago samunonita? Tepo awa. Na ge ago oko sane. Nera kota, na yaya ei awa umuro betamu sero osena.
\v 28 O Mama, ni zazo niso de ike ni.” Yesu meni ago senu utura ena ge ego osenua awa, “Na zazo naso de ike nitana, noko de ike namunona.”
\v 29 Ago senu ema dubu dopero itiwa ami niniro ego sewa awa, “Tarara gatetia.” Ota eni meni ego sewa awa, “Angelo zo meni ge numore sesi, tanita.”
\v 30 Ago sewa Yesu meni nusokare nana bera puro ego senua awa, “Ge awa namore kota, nikare emo kei awetia.
\v 31 Zeme Anutu meni zebura ema bama awina-dawina wamunoya. Zeme na zebu emira tua* dereniro masi nuso pumamunona.
\v 32 Nukare na zebura ena puro witi ike nara* zebu serora ema bama zumana naso nana mamunora.” Ago senua awa.
\v 33 Awa betai nogo betamu inoinu amira ge awa senua.
\v 34 Ago senu ema itiwa ami ego sewa awa, “Nakare ge gayai itia amira ego gosinowenakare awa: Soyai Ema nasokare Kristo nu kaka betamu nuai gege nuamunoya. Ata nine meni awa ego tosa, ‘Emara Mai puro witiro nira ikonamunora.’ Nogoro ago tosi? Emara Mai aweni?”
\v 35 Ago sewa Yesu meni ge ina ego senua awa, “Zasimai meni nisokare nana ena be apunu-kaka gege zasimamunoya awa. Are mume meni nikare dowai azu, zasimai itai zasimaire noiwo. Zo nu mumera susawise ebata oko gosinoya.
\v 36 Are zasimai nisokare nana itai duba meni tuma didinoise dubu nuso wero noiwo.” Yesu meni ge ago sero nukare doro baro bezero noisonua awa.
\s1 Yuda ema dainiro meni Yesu kaka tuma diamu wewa.
\p 
\v 37 Yesu nu tani putoure dainiro nusokare nana giti mokara wero munu gosinoise nu tuma kaka diamu wewa awa.
\v 38 Awa porofete Yesayara ge me waise ago ine wewa awa. Nu ge ego gaenua awa,
\li2 Tua, oziga niso sawenakare ai meni
\li2 gawi me inowi? Tua meni putou nuso
\li2 are kereninu?
\v 39 Are nukare Yesura ge niniro nu tuma diai ine tepo wewa. Nera kota, Yesayara ge gayai zo itinua. Ge awa ego ewa,
\li1 
\v 40 Anutu meni ego senua awa,
\li2 “Nukare giti moka meni nena gai azu, o duba meni nena kotumuro gai azu, o duba nusokare kapetenara na nukare kora wai azu.” Anutu meni ago sero senu giti moka nusokare guma wenua, ota nu duba nusokare gazenu omata ine wenua.
\v 41 Yesaya meni ge awa gaenua. Nera kota, nu Yesura simai zasimaire giro ge awa Yesure senua awa.
\p 
\v 42 Yuda emara gita wai ema dainiro meni Yesu tuma diwa. Ata nukare tuma diai nusokare kerenara Farisayo meni nukare yere ibura ena esenai azu, tuma diai bezero noisowa awa.
\v 43 Ago wewa, nera kota, Anutu meni nukare bowi waise awa yaba pei-kaka inoisowa. Ata ema meni nukare bowi warise awa yaba bamubake inoisowa awa.
\p 
\v 44 Yesu meni zawa sero ego senua awa, “Zo nu na tuma diamunoya ami na gege kota, na senu osena nu awa dai tuma diamunoya.
\v 45 Ota zo nu na gamunoya ami na senu osena awa dai gamunoya.
\v 46 Zo nu na tuma diamunoya ami mumera itai azu sero na zasimai ine ami zebura osena awa.
\v 47 Zo nu ge naso niniro kaka dimamu duamunoya nu awa nane oko gera potamunona. Na ema gera potamu kota, korawamu osena awa.
\v 48 Zo nu ge naso niniro doro na azu samunoya amira zas itia. Ge towena ami ama be bamura ena zas nuso wamunoya.
\v 49 Nera kota, na ge towena, awa duba nasora oko towena. Mama na senu osena ami ge sanise sero na tugata-magata wenua awa.
\v 50 Na ego gosinowena: Mamera ge meni nuai me ewanana tapinowia. Are ge towena awa Mama meni sero gipenua te towena awa.” Ago senua awa.
\c 13
\s1 Yesu meni bua mai nusora te sewenua.
\p 
\v 1 Betai Daininua amira pura be zora awinoinu Yesu nu nutope ego ginua awa, “Na zebu doro ewesemuro Mamera nana witamunona amira be zora awinoya.” Ago gosinoise giro bua mai nuso zebura noisowa awa dubara dumi pumunua. Dumi pumai nuso awa kaka tepo wamu.
\p 
\v 2 Pire nukare nena namu auniro itiwa tani ego ine kei awenua. Simonra mai Yudas Iskeriot nu Yesu kerenaise Satan meni kotumai awa emoko duba nusora potinu itinua awa.
\v 3 Are Yesu meni ego ginua awa: “Mama nu nena dapikarago wana nasora potinu itewia. Na Anutura nana ena osena, noko Anutura nana ewesemuro witamunona.”
\v 4 Kotumai ago gosinoise nena ninoinua awa doro eriro tama woi nuso tame awa dutero poti enibara niro tauli zo puro ipune awero
\v 5 ou tewara zozero bua mai nusora te sewenua awa. Sewero tauli ipune itinua ami te nusokare gaenua.
\v 6 Ago inoise mai enira te sewero amire Simon Petorora te sewamu wenu nu ego senua awa, “Ni Tua meni te naso sewamu tosa?”
\v 7 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Tani inona emira susu ni oko gosinosa. Noma ama gamunosa.”
\v 8 Ago senu Petoro meni ego senua awa, “Tepo awa. Ni te naso oko sewamunosa.” Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na te niso kaka sewamu wana ni namore dai duba da wero oko nuamunosa.”
\v 9 Ago senu Simon Petoro meni ina ego senua awa, “Tua, ago sero giro te naso gege kota, wanere gitire dai sewe.”
\v 10 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Zo nu ou gutero noma te nuso gege sewai tama saramamunoya. Nikare saramai. Ata nisokare nana zo meni saramaire oko nowia.”
\v 11 Nu kerenai ema awa gosinoise amire ego senua awa, “Nisokare nana zo meni saramaire oko nowia.”
\s1 Te sewaira susu senu giwa.
\p 
\v 12 Yesu meni te nusokare sewero pesuniro tama woi nuso iboi noko wosuniro arumuro itise ego senua awa, “Na nena nimorekare wetena amira susu gosinowita?
\v 13 Nikare namore gipai ema asise, o Tua asise awinoise nowewa. Na ago wero nowena, are me towewa.
\v 14 Are na Tua nisokare o gipai ema nisokare meni na natope puro osisinoise te nisokare sewetena giro nikare nitopekare puro osisinoise te ina-sewa inoise nuawa te wamunoya.
\v 15 Na tani nimorekare gipetena awa puro noise na wetena da ago ine inoise noiwo.
\v 16 Na me memeka sana niniu. Soumai zo meni ema tua nusora nuai awa dainiro nuai ine oko itia. Ota buara senu bamunua ami buara mama dainai ine oko itia.
\v 17 Are nikare ge awa niniro baitiro amira te nuamunowa, awa nikare yawa sara wamunowa.
\p 
\v 18 Na ge sesena ami nikare dapikarago oko pupinoya. Dubu sianiro pumuna nikare awa gosinona. Ata ge gayai zo ego itia awa me waise sai itia, ‘Ma ewawena ninowia ami na damu toya.’
\v 19 Tani awa kaka kei awamure na nikare bere-bere tugata inona. Are ama tani awa kei awai amire nikare namore ego sewo, ‘Nu me Soyai Ema nasokai Kristo.’
\v 20 Na me memeka sane. Zo nu nikare buara potina awa sawa diamunoya ami buara mama na sawa dia ago ine wamunoya. Zo nu na sawa diamunoya ami na senu osena nu awa dai sawa dia ago ine wamunoya.
\s1 Yesu meni Yudasra susu kereninua.
\p 
\v 21 Yesu nu ge ago sero moka nuso waya wenu giro kereniro ego senua awa, “Na me memeka nimorekare sane. Nisokare nana zo meni na kereniro iwora nana wanera potamunoya.”
\v 22 Ago senu bua mai nuso nukare ina-ga wero are toi asero kau wewa awa.
\v 23 Are mai zo Yesura nana zorage itinua. Yesu nu ara tapinoisonua.
\v 24 Are Simon Petoro meni giti-awa meni etete wero ego senua awa, “Atata we sai gase. Are toi?”
\v 25 Ago senu mai ami Yesu nana zorage baro be dane potiro ego senua awa, “Tua, ni are tosi?”
\v 26 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Porong sura patiro potana namunoya nu amire tona.” Ago sero porong sura patiro Simonra mai Yudas Iskeriot amire potinu ninua awa.
\v 27 Ninu Satan meni moka nusora toinua awa. Ago wenu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Tani wamu tosa awa eya weyo.”
\v 28 Ge ago Yudasre senu eni dai itiwa ami gera susu kaka gamu wewa awa.
\v 29 Eni meni ego sewa awa, “Yudas nu moni nasokai dia inowia, are nu pura emira nena zo paise sesi susawita? Ota ema bogamasare moni kanowaise toi?” Ago sewa awa.
\v 30 Yudas nu porong niro eya eriro pi mumere bamunua awa.
\s1 Potai ge seka.
\p 
\v 31 Yudas bamunu Yesu meni bua mai enire ego senua awa, “Emara Mai amira zazo de ike naira be zeme zora awetia. Tani naso nana kei awamunoya ami Anutura zazo de ike namunoya.
\v 32 Are na Emara Mai meni Anutura zazo de ike nana nu nutope zazo naso de ike namunoya. Agoro be iboi tepo, eya de ike namunoya.
\v 33 O mai awiso naso, na be apunu-kaka nimorekare dai nuamunona. Ama nikare na kau wamunowa. Are na Yuda ema enire sisena da ago ine nimorekare sane. Na bayamunona amira nikare bayai ine oko itia.
\v 34 Are na potai ge seka zo nimorekare potitinona. Dubara dumi ina-pa wewo. Na nikare dubara dumi pumawena nowewa ago ine nitopekare dubara dumi ina-pa inoise noiwo.
\v 35 Nikare dubara dumi ina-pa inoise nuawa ema nikare giro Yesura bua mai wero nora asamunora.” Ago senua awa.
\s1 Yesu meni Petoro nu begi wamu inoinua amira ge senua.
\p 
\v 36 Ago senu Simon Petoro meni atata wero ego senua awa, “Tua, ni nago bayamunosi?” Ago atata wenu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na bayamunona amira ni zeme emire bayai ine oko itia. Noma ama bayamunosa.”
\v 37 Ago senu Petoro meni ego senua awa, “Tua, ni nera na zeme nimore dai bayai ine oko itia asinosi? Na ni emo inoise nuai naso sisamunona te awa.”
\v 38 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Ni na emo nuai niso sisamu tosa? Na me memeka sane. Kokara ge kaka samure nine na begi wasa be etorobara wamunoya.” Ago senua awa.
\c 14
\s1 Anutura nana bayai amira ebata awa Yesu.
\p 
\v 1 Yesu meni bua mai nusore ego senua awa, “Nikare duba nisokare oko sisawe. Nikare Anutu tuma didinoise na dai tuma diwo.
\v 2 Mama nasora nata amira ibu-mara dainiro itera. Ago kaka itamu sia, awa na itai zara nisokare sia wamu bayamunona ago oko samena.
\v 3 Are na baro itai zara nisokare sia wero noko kapeteniro muro nikare uzumana baro na nuamunona da amira nuamunowa.
\v 4 Bayamunona amira ebata awa gosinowewa.”
\v 5 Ago senu Tomas meni ina ego senua awa, “Tua, ni nago bayamunosi, awa nakare kaka gamu inonakare. Are nogo wero ebata gamunonikare?”
\v 6 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Ebata Mamera nana bayai awa na ewa. Ge me kerenai awa na ewa. Nuai seka potai awa na ewa. Na dainiro Mamera nana kei awai ine oko itia.
\v 7 Nikare susu naso gamewa sia, awa nikare Mama nasora susu da ago gamewa. Zeme nikare Mama nasora susu gewa kei awinoya.”
\p 
\v 8 Ago senu Filip meni ego senua awa, “Ni Mama gipasa giro te asamunonakare.”
\v 9 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Filip, na be iboi-tatana nimorekare dai nuawena ni na kaka giro baitamu inowesita? Zo nu na gosinowia ami Mama gosinowia. Are ni nogoro, ‘Mama gipe ganekare,’ ago tosi?
\v 10 Mama meni naso nana itewia, da ago na Mamera nana itewena, awa gesa me kaka wamu inoita? Ge nimorekare tugata inowena awa duba nasora oko tugata inowena. Mama meni duba nasora noise bua nuso inowia.
\v 11 Mama meni namore itewia, o na da ago Mamere itewena ge awa niniwo me wae. Ota ge awa gawa me kaka wamu wai giro tani inowena awa kotumuro amire ge awa giwo me wae.
\s1 Ozana osamunoya amira ge senua.
\p 
\v 12 Na me memeka sana niniu. Zo nu na tuma diamunoya ami bua inowena da awa wamunoya. Na Mamera nana witamunona, are nu bua awa gege kota, wai nama awa dainiro bamu wamunoya.
\v 13 Nikare zazo naso puro noise isa sawa te ninitinoise wamunona. Awa Mamera bowi kei awaise sero na Mai meni ago wamunona.
\v 14 Nikare zazo naso puro noise na nena zo emo begomo sawa ninitinoise ago wamunona.
\v 15 Ara tamai nisokare naso nana itamunoya, awa nikare ge naso dimamunowa.
\v 16 Nane Mama begomo sana nu Soremai nisokare zo potai osero nimorekare dai nuai gege nuamunoya.
\v 17 Nu awa Ozana. Nu ge me susure nimorekare gipamunoya. Ema na tuma kaka diamu inowera ami Ozana giti moka nusokare meni oko gosinowera. Noko nukare nu kotumai meni oko gosinowera. Are nukare Ozana puro nuai ine tepo. Ata nu nimorekare dai nowia, ota moka nisokarera toiro nuamunoya. Are nikare nu giro baititinowewa.
\v 18 Na nikare duana popoiwo oko wero nuamunowa. Na nisokare nana noko ewesemuro mamunona.
\v 19 Be apunu-kaka zo itia awa tepo wai amire ema na tuma kaka diamu nowera ami na noko oko gamunora. Ata ninekare na gamunowa. Na nuai gege nowena, are nikare dai nuamunowa awa.
\v 20 Ozana meni ose nisokare nana nai amire Mama meni namore dai nowia, ota na nimorekare dai nowena, ota nikare namore dai nowewa, amira susu awa giro baitamunowa.
\p 
\v 21 Zo nu bera ge naso niniro puro dipinoise nowia amira ara tamai awa naso nana itia. Are zo nu na ara tapinowia, da ago ine Mama naso meni nu ara tamamunoya. Ota nane da ago nu ara tapinoise susu naso numore kerenamunona.”
\v 22 Ago senu Yudas Iskeriot amira zazo meni atata wero ego senua awa, “Tua, ni nogo wero susu niso namorekare gege kerenitinoise ema eni bamu amire kaka kerenamu bezamunosi?”
\v 23 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Zo nu na ara tamamunoya ami ge naso niniro dimamunoya. Ago wai Mama naso meni nu ara tamamunoya. Ago inoise nato Mamere nuso nana kei awero nuamunonato awa.
\v 24 Zo nu na ara kaka tamamu wamunoya ami ge naso oko dimamunoya. Ota ge tugata wawena gosinowewa awa naso kota, Mama na iyetinua amira nana ena tupewia awa.
\s1 Yesu meni duba-ozaire nuai awa potai pumamunonakai.
\p 
\v 25 Na nimorekare dai noise ge ago ine tugata-magata inowena awa.
\v 26 Ota Soremai nisokare Ozana awa nu Mama meni be nasora iyetai osero ge dapikarago nimorekare tugata-magata wamunoya. Ge nane tugata inowena da awa Ozana meni awa-uzero tepo wamunoya.
\v 27 Na duba-ozaire nuai awa nimorekare potitinona. Na duba-ozaire nuai naka naso awa nimorekare potitinona. Zebura ema meni potitinowera ago ine kota, duba-ozaire nuai naso me awa nimorekare potitinona. Are duba nisokare azu wai tepo, kotumu-katumu wai tepo, itarise.
\v 28 Na ego sesena ninewa awa. Na nikare doro baro noma noko nisokare nana ewesemuro mamunona. Nikare na ara tamamewa sia, awa na Mamera nana witamunona awa giro yawa sara wamewa. Nera kota, Mama nu witai naso nowia.
\v 29 Tani naso nana kei awamunoya awa kaka kei awamure gita nimorekare tona. Are kei awai amire tuma diai nisokare zewai waise.
\v 30 Na ge dainiro susumuro nimorekare oko samunona. Zebura tua Satan meni naso nana mamu inoise inoya. Ata nu namore tani zo wai ine tepo.
\v 31 Ema na tuma kaka diamu inowera ami ara tamai naso Mamera nana itia awa garise sero bua ge towia awa inowena. Are eriu bayanekai.” Ago senua awa.
\c 15
\s1 Yesu nu wain susu. Nakai bona-wagana.
\p 
\v 1 Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Na wain susu me. Mama naso meni wain buara mama.
\v 2 Bona zo naso nana itise me kaka ziamu wai giro kapero duamunoya. Ota bona zo mere itai giro me dainiro ziaise sero kapero kora wai saramamunoya.
\v 3 Nikare awa ge tugata wena niniwa, are Mama naso meni waya nisokare kapero nikare kora wenu saramuro nowewa.
\v 4 Are nikare namore dai nuawa na da ago nimorekare dai nuamunona. Wain bona meni susure kaka gamamu nu gege itise me oko ziamunoya. Are nikare da ago ine namore kaka tayamu inoise me oko ziamunowa.
\v 5 Na awa wain susu. Nikare awa bona-wagana. Zo nu naso nana susumuro nuamunoya, awa na da ago nuso nana susumuro nuamunona. Ago wana nu me witai ziamunoya. Nikare na doro noise Anutura bua zo wai ine oko itia.
\v 6 Zo nu naso nana kaka susumamu wamunoya, nu awa duamunona. Ago wana wain bona duawera amawi sianiro niaora potawera awinowia ago ine wamunoya.
\v 7 Nikare naso nana susumuro ge naso poti dube niro nuamunowa, awa nena zota zo emo begomo sawa nisokare nana kei awamunoya.
\v 8 Nikare me bamubake zizinoise bua mai naso wero nuawa Mama nasora bowi kei awamunoya.
\s1 Ara tamaira ge.
\p 
\v 9 Mama meni na ara tapinowia, da ago ine nane nikare ara tapinowena. Are nikare ara tamai nasora noiwo.
\v 10 Na Mama nasora ge dipinowena, are ara tamai nuso naso nana itewia. Da ago ine nikare ge naso dimamunowa, awa ara tamai naso nisokare nana itamunoya.
\p 
\v 11 Yawa sara wai naso meni nisokare nana itai amire yawa sara nisokare meni moka nisokarera be muro itaise sero ge awa sesena.
\v 12 Potai ge naso ego itia awa: Na nikare ara tapinowena, da ago ine nitopekare ara ina-tama inoise noiwo.
\v 13 Zo nu otao mamai nuso soyamu wero giro nuai nuso nukare emo doro betamunoya amira ara tamai awa ara tamai me asamunora.
\v 14 Ge potitinowena awa dimamunowa, awa nikare otao mamai naso wamunowa.
\v 15 Na be zeme emire nimorekare soumai oko tona. Nera kota, soumai meni ema tua nusora kotumai itewia awa oko gosinowia. Na nikare soumai kota, otao mamai naso asinona. Nera kota, nane Mama nasora nana ena ge ninina awa te kereniro tugata wero tepo watana. Are na nikare gena otao mamai naso inowa awa.
\v 16 Ninekare na buara bayanise sero oko pumuwa. Nane nikare buara bayawise sero pumuna. Are nikare baro buara me bamubake ziawise sena awa. Are me ziawa itai gege itaise. Ago wero zazo naso puro noise Mama begomo sawa te potamunoya.
\v 17 Nikare nitopekare ara ina-tama inoise noiwo. Ge awa potai ge naso awa.
\s1 Nukare Yesu iwo wewa, are nukare bua mai nuso dai iwo wamunora.
\p 
\v 18 Ema ge naso kaka ninamu ami nikare iwo wara amire ego sewo, ‘Gita Tua ago zaawero iwo wewa.’
\v 19 Ema ge naso kaka ninamu amira mokara toyamewa sia, awa nukare nikare saore giro nimorekare otao wamera. Ata na nikare nusokare nana dubura ena sianiro pumuna nuai nusokare dowa, are nukare nikare iwo inowera awa.
\v 20 Ge zo nimorekare ego sesena awa kotumuwo: Soumai meni ema tua nusora nuai awa nune dainiro nuai ine oko itia. Ge amira susu ego ewa. Eni meni ge naso niniro dipinora, da ago ine eni meni ge nisokare niniro dimamunora. Ota eni meni na iwo inora, da ago ine eni meni nikare iwo wamunora.
\v 21 Nukare nu na iyetinua awa kaka gamu inowera, are da ago ine nimorekare wamunora. Nikare bua mai naso, are ago ine wamunora.
\v 22 Na nusokare nana kaka osamu wamena, ota susu naso kaka tugata wamu wamena, awa nukare pasina amu nuamera. Ota zeme nukare pasina nusokare nogo nogo sero bezamunori?
\v 23 Zo nu na iwo inowia ami da ago ine Mama naso iwo inowia.
\v 24 Na nusokare nana noise tani putoure ema meni wai ine tepo awa kaka wamu wamena, awa nukare pasina amu nuamera. Ata nukare tani putoure inowena awa giro na iwo inoise Mama naso da ago iwo inowera.
\v 25 Ago wawera ge zo lo buku nusokarera gayai itewia awa me inowia. Ge awa ego ewa: ‘Nukare na tepo iwo wewa.’
\p 
\v 26 Ata Soremai nisokare Mamera nana itewia awa iyetana Mamera nana ena osero nikare sorepitinoise susu naso nimorekare kerenamunoya. Nu awa Ozana. Ge me saira mama numa awa.
\v 27 Ota nikare be bua zaawena amira ana namore dai nowewa ami dai susu naso kerenamunowa.
\c 16
\p 
\v 1 Ama nukare nena mou-mau nimorekare wara nikare itazaita wero tuma diai nisokare besai azu, na ge ei awa bere-bere kerenitinona awa.
\v 2 Nukare yere ibu soyamunora. Awa daba kota, be zo mamunoya be amire nukare ‘Anutura bua inowenakare’ asinoise nikare dara bebetenamunowa.
\v 3 Nukare nato Mamere awa kaka giro baitamu inowera, are ago ine wamunora.
\v 4 Ge tona ami me wai amire, ‘Yesu gita namorekai ago senua,’ ago sawise sero nikare bere-bere tugata inona.
\s1 Ozanara bua amira ge.
\p Na nikare gipamu sero bua zaawero noina be amire be naso iboi itinua, are na ge awa gita nimorekare kaka samu noisona.
\v 5 Ata zeme meni awa na senu osena amira nana witamu sero inona, are ge awa sesena. Ata nisokare nana zo meni na ego kaka atata wamu inoya, ‘Ni nago bayamunosi?’
\v 6 Ge ago ine nimorekare sesena, are duba nai meni moka nisokare bera muro itia.
\v 7 Na ge me sana niniu. Na ewesemuro witamunona, awa nikare kokopai itawise sero witamunona. Na kaka witamu wamunona, awa Soremai meni oko osamunoya. Ata na witiro iyetana osero nimorekare dai nuamunoya.
\v 8 Osero nena etorobara amira susu awa eramare kerenamunoya: pasinara susu, ata ewanana wero nuaira susu, ata pasinara ina tamai amira susu. Nu susu etorobara awa kerenai eraa meni gara me wamunoya.
\v 9 Pasinara susu ego ine gipai gamunora: nukare na kaka tuma diamu inowera, are pasina nusokare dago itewia.
\v 10 Ewanana wero nuaira susu ego ine gipai gamunora: na Mamera nana ewesemuro witana nikare na noko oko gamunowa.
\v 11 Pasinara ina tamai amira susu ego ine gipai gamunora: zebu emira tua awa Anutura kotora ena duwaise sai itia.
\p 
\v 12 Ge tugata wai naso dainiro dago itia, ata nikare zeme ninai ine tepo.
\v 13 Ge me susure sai awa Ozana awa. Nune osero ge me dapikarago susure nimorekare gipamunoya. Ota ge awa kotumai nusora oko puro samunoya. Ge naneto Mamere samunonato awa niniro te nikare tugata wamunoya. Tani eure-taure ama kei awamunora awa dai bere-bere nimorekare kerenamunoya.
\v 14 Na ge sana Ozana meni niniro puro nimorekare kerenamunoya. Ago wai bowi naso kei awamunoya awa.
\v 15 Mamera nena dapikarago awa nena naso, ami emo na nimorekare ego sesena awa, ‘Ozana meni nena naso puro nimorekare kerenamunoya.’
\s1 Yesu nu baro noko ewesemuro mamunoya.
\p 
\v 16 Be apunu-kaka itia awa tepo wai amire nikare na oko gamunowa. Noko be apunu-kaka tepo wai amire nikare na gamunowa.”
\v 17 Yesu meni ago senu bua mai nuso nutopekare ge ina-sa wero ego sewa awa, “Nu ego toya, ‘Be apunu-kaka itia awa tepo wai amire nikare na oko gamunowa. Noko be apunu-kaka tepo wai amire nikare na gamunowa.’ Nu nogoro ago toi? Ota nu ge zo dai ego sesia awa, ‘Na Mamera nana witamunona.’ Ago sesia awa.”
\v 18 Bua mai meni ago sero noko ego sewa awa, “Nu ego sesia, ‘Be apunu-kaka itia.’ Ago awa nogoro toi, nakai sirinonakai.”
\v 19 Ago sero nu atata wamu sero wewa Yesu nu nutope giro ego senua awa, “Ge ego nimorekare sesena amira ina-sa inowita? ‘Be apunu-kaka itia awa tepo wai amire nikare na oko gamunowa. Noko be apunu-kaka tepo wai amire nikare na gamunowa.’ Ge amira susu sana gamu towita?
\v 20 Na me memeka nimorekare tona. Nikare dire-buare inuawa ema na tuma kaka diamu ami yawa sara wamunora. Nikare duba naire nuawa duba nai nisokare meni kapetenai yawa sara wai nisokare nana kei awamunoya.
\v 21 Bama meni mai pamu inoma yaya tapinoise duba nitinowera. Ago inoma mai puro oreniro ‘mai pumena’ asero yawa sara inowera. Yaya tapinowera awa oko kotupitinowera.
\v 22 Da ago ine nikare zeme duba nitinowa. Ata na nikare noko gamunona be amire nikare yawa sara bamubake wamunowa. Yawa sara nisokare awa ema zo meni kapai tepo wai ine tepo.
\v 23 Are be amire nikare nena zo kau wero giro na oko atata wamunowa. Na me memeka sane. Nikare nena zo emo Mama begomo sawa nena awa potamunoya. Awa nera kota, nu na emo inoise potamunoya.
\v 24 Noisonakai amira ana tupise nikare zazo naso puro noise nena zo emo begomo kaka samu. Are yawa sara wai meni nisokare nana kei awero be muro itaise begomo seu. Begomo sawa potai pamunowa awa.
\s1 Yesura zazo puro noise Anutu begomo sai.
\p 
\v 25 Ge nimorekare tugata wero tupewena awa ge bezai tugata inowena. Noma be zo mamunoya amire na ge bezai meni awa oko samunona. Be amire na Mamera susu poti damu namu ge bezero kota, me kereniro nimorekare samunona.
\v 26 Be amire nikare zazo naso puro noise Mama begomo samunowa. Na ego oko tona, ‘Nane nikare soremuro Mama begomo samunona.’ Awa oko tona. Awa nera kota, Mama meni nikare ara tapinowia.
\v 27 Na Mamera nana ena osena ge awa nikare niniwa me wenu na ara tapinowewa. Are Mama meni da ago ine nikare ara tapinowia.
\v 28 Na Mama doro zebura osena, are na zebu doro noko Mamera nana wititinona.”
\v 29 Ago senu bua mai nuso meni ego sewa awa, “Ni zeme ge bezai doro damu-damuke kereniro tosa awa.
\v 30 Are nimore ego gosinonakare: ni nitope nena dapikarago giro tepo inowesa. Nakare ni atata wamu kotupitinuawenakare ni nitope gosinowesa, ami emo ni Anutura nana ena osesa awa genakare me inoya.”
\v 31 Ago sewa Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Nikare zeme gewa me inoita?
\v 32 Be zo itia awa eya mai amire na doro bozero nata nisokare sero baro tepo wamunowa. Ago wero na duawa na imata nuamunona. Ata na imata oko nuamunona. Mama meni namore dai nowia, are imata oko nuamunona.
\v 33 Nikare azu doro oreniro nuawise sero ge ei awa nimorekare sesena. Nikare zebura yayare duba naire nuamunowa. Ata nane zebura nena dire-bere awa puro osero patitinona, are nikare putoure noiwo.” Ago senua awa.
\c 17
\s1 Yesu nu nutope begomo senua.
\p 
\v 1 Yesu nu ge awa sero tepo wero iri utura niro begomo toise ego senua awa, “Mama, be zora awinoya. Na Mai niso. Na zazo niso de ike nana bamu waise sero gita nine zazo naso de ike nasa bamu waise tona.
\v 2 Ni ema eni namore potisa. Potiro na nuai me ewanana awa numorekare potanise sero na zebu serora ema bama amira mama bamubake potisa.
\v 3 Nuai me ewanana amira susu ego itia: Ni Anutu me daimata. Ema iyetisa awa Yesu Kristo awa. Ema bama meni namorege gara me wai nukare nuai me ewanana pumamunora.
\v 4 Bua ge namore sesa awa wero tupie pesunitinona. Ago inoise zazo niso de ike nitana.
\v 5 O Mama, zebu kaka kei awamure na nimore dai utu zasimai nasore noisona, da awa noko potiyo na puro nuane.
\s1 Yesu meni bua mai nuso emo begomo senua.
\p 
\v 6 Erama dapikarago amira nana ena ema eni sianiro namore potisa naso wewa. Are na susu niso numorekare kerenisena. Dubu niso asai noiwa awa namore potisa nukare ge niso niniro puro poti dube niro nowera.
\v 7 Nukare zeme nena naso dapikarago niso nana ena gege tupewia awa gosinowera.
\v 8 Ni ge namore potisa awa sena niniro pumuwa awa. Ago inoise niso nana ena osena awa giro me asewa awa, are nine bua ge namore sesa awa da ago niniwa me wenua awa.
\v 9 Na nukare emo nimore begomo tona awa. Ema na tuma kaka diamu inowera nukare ami emo oko nimore begomo tona. Dubu namore potisa ami emo isa tona. Nera kota, nukare awa dubu niso me awa.
\v 10 Ema naso dapikarago awa niso awa. Ota ema niso dapikarago awa naso awa. Are nukare zazo naso de ike nitinora.
\v 11 Nane niso nana muro zebura oko itamunona. Ata nukare meni awa zebura itise nuamunora. O Mama saramai, nage duba da wero nowenage, da ago ine nukare duba da wero nuarise sero ni zazo niso namore potisa amira putou meni nukare dia weyo.
\v 12 Na numorekare dai noise zazo nisora putou meni nukare dia inowena. Ni zazo awa namore potisa. Na nukare dia wero baititana, are zo meni kaka tara awamu. Ota ge gayai zo itia awa me waise daimata meni tara awero sisamunoya. Nu tara awaira gegenai.
\v 13 Yawa sara wai naso meni duba nusokare topetaise sero na zebura itise niso nana mamu inoise ge ewa tona.
\v 14 Na ge niso potawena puro nuawera zebura ema meni nukare iwo inowera. Nuai naso awa zebura ema amira nuai ine oko aewa. Da ago ine nuai nusokare awa zebura ema amira nuai ine oko aewa. Are zebura ema meni nukare iwo inowera.
\v 15 Ni bua mai naso awa zebu emira ena soero pumasise kota, Satan meni nukare waya wai azu, ni nukare soremasise begomo tona ewa.
\v 16 Nuai naso awa zebura ema amira nuai ine oko aewa. Da ago ine nuai nusokare awa zebura ema amira nuai ine oko aewa.
\v 17 Ge niso me meni duba nusokare ziai dopero itai nukare saramuro gegenai niso warise. Ge niso awa ge me susure awa.
\v 18 Nine na zebura ena bua wanise sesa, are da ago ine nane nukare zebura ena bua warise sena awa.
\v 19 Ge me meni duba nusokare ziai zewai wai nuarise na nuai naso nukare emo wana nisora potitinona ewa.
\s1 Yesu meni ema ge ninai nakai emo begomo senua.
\p 
\v 20 Ota na nukare emo gege oko begomo tona. Ge tugata wara niniro na tuma diamunora nukare emo dai begomo tona.
\v 21 Nukare duba da wero nuarise nimore begomo tona. O Mama, ni namore itewesa na da ago nimore itewena, da ago ine nukare namorege dai itarise. Ago wara ema na tuma kaka diamu inowera ami nine na iyetisa osena awa giro me asare.
\v 22 Nage duba da wero nowenage, da ago ine nukare duba da wero nuarise sero ni putou namore potisa da awa numorekare potitinona.
\v 23 Na numorekare dai itana ni da ago namore dai itasa nukare duba meni puniro daimata wero nuare. Ago wero nuara ema na tuma kaka diamu inowera ami na iyetisa osena awa garise. Agoro nine na duba meni punitinoise nukare dai punitinowesa awa giro baitarise.
\p 
\v 24 O Mama, ema dubu namore potisa nukare awa na nuamunona da amira nuarise tona. Ago wero zebura siwako kaka kei awamure nine na ara tapinoise utura zasimai namore potisa zasimai awa namorege dai noise garise tona.
\v 25 O Mama, ni saramaira mama. Ema na tuma kaka diamu inowera ami ni oko giro baititinowera. Nane meni awa ni giro baititinowena. Ota dubu naso meni nine na iyetisa osena awa giro baititinowera.
\v 26 Ara tamai niso naso nana itewia da ami nusokare nana itai na numorekare dai nuamu sero oziga ge niso numorekare kerenitana. Ago gege kerenitinoise nuamunona.” Ago senua awa.
\c 18
\s1 Yesu ni buara noinu pumuwa.
\p 
\v 1 Yesu nu begomora ge awa senu tepo wenu eriro bua mai nuso pumuro nate ena osero ou Kidoron semuro zebu zora ni bua itisonua amira bamuwa.
\v 2 Yesu bua mai nusore nukare be eyaya ago aunitinoisowa, are Yudas kerenai ema ami ni bua awa nu gai awa.
\v 3 Are Yesu bua mai nusore ago noiwa Yudas kerenai ema ami pris babezinomare Farisayore amira polis eni ata soldia eni awa puro gita wenu bana izimuro lam gaero gi ami puro bamuwa awa.
\v 4 Yesu meni nena dapikarago numore wamu inoiwa awa giro eriro gita baro nukare tamuro atata wero ego senua awa, “Nikare aware kau inowi?”
\v 5 Ago senu nukare ego sewa awa, “Nasaretera ema zo zazo nuso Yesu awa kau inonakare.” Ago sewa nu ego senua awa, “Na ewa.” Ago senua awa. Yudas kerenai ema awa soldiare dai dopero itinua awa.
\v 6 Are Yesu meni, “Na ewa,” ago senu nukare azu atune baro duuwa awa.
\v 7 Ago wewa noko atata wero ego senua awa, “Nikare aware kau inowi?” Ago senu nukare ego sewa awa, “Yesu Nasaretera ema.”
\v 8 Ago sewa Yesu meni numorekare ego senua awa, “Na sesena awa. Na ewa. Nikare na kau inowa, are dubu naso awa dou bayare.”
\v 9 Nu ge gita senua awa me waise sero bua mai nuso duarise senua. Ge gita ego senua awa, “Namore potisa nukare dia wetena zo da kaka tara awamu awa.”
\p 
\v 10 Are Simon Petoro nu kasiwa egira puro noinua awa zinu kisimunu pris bamura soumai zo amira dana wana mera awa kesenua. Mai awa zazo nuso Maliko.
\v 11 Ago wenu Yesu meni Petorore ego senua awa, “Kasiwa niso egira poti toyae. Yaya ei awa Mama naso meni namore potitinoya, awa azu duanise inosita?” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 12 Ago senu soldiara dia wai meni senu soldia ata Yudara polis ami Yesu puro wana beniwa awa.
\v 13 Beniro puro gita bamu Anasira nana sora niwa awa. Zepa amire ema zo zazo nuso Kayafa ami pris bamu wero noisonua. Nune Anasira mai bama diri atiro noisonua.
\v 14 Kayafa nune gita Yuda emare ge ego senua awa, “Ema nakai dapikarago waya wero tepo wai azu, nu daimata ami nakai emo betaise sai itia.” Gita ago senua awa.
\s1 Petoro meni Yesu begi wenua.
\p 
\v 15 Polis meni Yesu poti Anasira nana niwa Simon Petoroto otao nuso zore nuto Yesu puro bamuwa awa ama ganero bamuwato awa. Petorora otao* awa pris bamu meni gosinoinsonua, are Yesu ama ganero toi goma mokara ninua awa.
\v 16 Petoro meni awa goma atune dopenua awa. Ago wenu otao nuso meni awa pris bamura nana sora noisonua, are osero goma be dia wai mai bama diri zo amire senu goma be piaka ninu Petoro toi mokara ninua awa.
\v 17 Petoro toinu mai bama diri goma be dia wai ami Petoro giro ego senua awa, “Ema omira bua mai zo ni awani, tanita?” Ago senu Petoro meni ego senua awa, “Na tepo.”
\v 18 Pris bamura soumaire soldiare nukare zazama wenu giro ni wero awinoiwa Petoro nu da ago bamu nusokare nana soe niro ni awenua awa.
\s1 Pris bamu meni Yesu atata wenua.
\p 
\v 19 Pris bamu meni Yesu bua mai pumunua o ge tugata inoisonua amire atata wenua.
\v 20 Atata wenu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Na ge damu ena gege towena. Yuda ema aunitinowera — yere ibura enata ibu bamura ena — amira ena na ge sero tugata wise gipise awinowena. Na bezero ge oko towena.
\v 21 Are ni nogoro na atata inosi? Ge sawena ninitinowera nukare awa atata wasa ge towena awa sara ninase.”
\v 22 Ago senu dia ema dopero itiwa amira nana zo meni Yesu opewe dero ego senua awa, “Ni nogoro ge ago ine pris bamure tosi?”
\v 23 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Ge waya sesena sia tosa amira susu se gare. Ota na ge kokopai tona amira nogoro na doinosi?” Ago senua awa.
\v 24 Anasi meni senu Yesu beniro puro bamu pris bamu zo zazo nuso Kayafa amira nana niwa awa.
\s1 Petoro meni Yesu noko begi wenua.
\p 
\v 25 Simon Petoro nu ni awinoise itinu nukare nu noko atata wero ego sewa awa, “Bua mai nusora dubu amira nana zo ni awani, tanita?” Ago sewa nu begi wero ego senua awa, “Na tepo.”
\v 26 Ago senu pris bamura soumai zo, Petoro meni dana kesenua amira dikai zo, ami ego senua awa, “Ina ni ni buara ena Yesure dai dopero itesa geni, tanita?”
\v 27 Ago senu Petoro meni noko begi wenu amire kokara ge senua awa.
\s1 Nukare Yesu Pilatora nana puro bamuwa.
\p 
\v 28 Pina atinu nukare Yesu Kayafara nana sora ena puro osero bamu Roma ema zo nukare dia inoisonua amira nana niwa awa. Yuda ema nukare Betai Daininua amira bona namu sero inoiwa, are nukare pura sisai azu, nukare Pilatora nana sora kaka toyamu wewa. Awa nera kota, Yuda ema meni ego toise noisowa awa, “Duba nasokai bemitire wai azu, nakai ema Yudakora nana oko toyanekai.”
\v 29 Ago toisowa, are nukare dura dopewa Pilato meni kei damu niro nukare atata wero ego senua awa, “Ema ei awa pasina nera puro tupewi?”
\v 30 Ago senu nukare ego sewa awa, “Nu pasina kaka wamu nuamia, awa nakare niso nana oko puro mamenakare.”
\v 31 Ago sewa Pilato meni ego senua awa, “Lo ge nisokare itia amira te seu tepo wae.” Ago senu nukare ego sewa awa, “Nakare mai betarise sai tepo wai awa nasokare nana gazai itia. Nera kota, lo nisokare Roma emara ami gazinoya.* Ota nine sasa te wamunoya.” Ago sewa awa.
\v 32 Yuda ema ago wewa Yesu nu nutope gita, “Na ni pasinaira dara betamunona,” ago senua amira ge me wenua.
\p 
\v 33 Pilato meni so mokara baro Yesu zawa senu bamunu ego senua awa, “Ni Yuda emara ema tua ni?”
\v 34 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Ge awa duba nisora tosita eni meni oziga naso nimore sesera giro tosi?”
\v 35 Ago senu Pilato meni ego senua awa, “Na Yuda ema oko aewa. Ema mamana niso ata pris babezinoma ami ni naso nana potitinora. Ni ne wetesi?”
\v 36 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Na zebura ena ema tua oko wero nowena. Na zebura ena ema tua inoise nuamena, awa ema dubu naso meni gi ami puro na soremara Yuda ema na oko pamera. Tua wero nuaira bua naso awa zebura oko itia.”
\v 37 Ago senu Pilato meni ego senua awa, “Agoro ni ema tua zo ni?” Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Awa, are tosa awa. Na ema tua zo. Na ge me susure kerenamu sero osero zebura ena kei awena awa. Ge me yaba inowera ami ge naso ninitinowera.”
\v 38 Ago senu Pilato meni ina ego senua awa, “Ge me awa neni?” Ago sero kei damu niro Yuda emare ego senua awa, “Na ema emira pasina tamamu sero kau inomite zo kaka tamamu wetena.
\v 39 Ota tani nisokare zo itia. Betai Daininua amira pura nisokarera ena sawewa benai ema zo awa-diawena tepo susawewia. Are pura emire ninawa na Yuda emara ema tua nisokare awa-diana nuaise towita?”
\v 40 Ago senu nukare arero sewa awa, “Tepo awa. Nu kota, Barabas awa awa-diasa mae.” Ago sewa awa. Barabas nu mai dero bewana wai ema.
\c 19
\s1 Pilato meni Yesu betaise sero emara nana wanera potinua.
\p 
\v 1 Pilato meni senu soldia nukare Yesu asi dirinare meni dewa.
\v 2 Ago wero nu isimamu sero asi dirinare puro bubuna wero giti nusora wosuniwa awa. Ago wero tama woi izasewai zo dai wosuniwa awa.
\v 3 Ago wero bamu nuso nana zorage niro sowene doinoise ego sewa awa, “Waiko koko, Yuda emara ema tua.”
\p 
\v 4 Pilato meni noko kei damu niro Yuda emare ego senua wa, “Giu. Na nu puro nisokare nana tupena. Na pasina nuso tamamu sero kau inomite zo kaka tamamu wetena.”
\v 5 Ago senu Yesu nu asi dirinare bubuna wai amire tama woi izasewaire dai osero dopenu Pilato meni gipero ego senua awa, “Ema ewa giu.”
\v 6 Ago senu pris babezinomare soldia nusokarere ami giro arero ego sewa awa, “Ni pasinaira witaise, ni pasinaira witaise.” Ago sewa Pilato meni be nusokarera pumuro ego senua awa, “Na pasina nuso kau inona. Nu pasina tepo. Are nikakare nitopekare puro ni pasinaira deu.”
\v 7 Ago senu Yuda ema meni ego sewa awa, “Nu nutope, ‘Na Anutura mai,’ asinowia, are ema ago ine awa betarise lo ge nasokare amira sai itia, are betaise.”
\v 8 Ago sewa Pilato meni ge awa niniro azu bamubake wenua awa.
\v 9 Ago wero Yesu noko uzumuro so mokara puro baro atata wero senua awa, ‘Ni nana kei awesi?” Ago senu Yesu meni ina kaka samu donua.
\v 10 Ago wenu Pilato meni ego senua awa, “Ni ge namore kaka samu inosa, atonua. Nane sana nuamunosita ni pasinaira betamunosi, amira putou namore potai, awa ni kaka gamu inosita?”
\v 11 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Anutu meni putou awa nimore kaka potamu wamia, awa ni na betaira potai ine te oko wamia. Are na niso nana wanera potia amira pasina meni pasina niso dainitinoya.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 12 Ago senu Pilato meni ge awa niniro kei damu niro Yesu awa-diro duamu senu Yuda ema nukare arero ego sewa awa, “Ni ema nu awa awa-diro duaira samunosa, awa ni Romara ema tua Sisa amira otao noko oko nuamunosa. Zo nu nutope ema tua asamunoya ami Romara ema tua Sisa awa dainamunoya.”
\v 13 Ago sewa Pilato meni ge awa niniro giro senu Yesu puro kei damu niwa Pilato meni ge sai tepo wai masi nusora arumuro itinua awa. Masi awa omata meni nabero wai. Masi amira zazo Yuda ema meni Gabata asinoisowa awa.
\p 
\v 14 Are Yuda ema pura itamu sero nena sia inoiwa waiko soe dopenu Pilato meni masi nusora itise Yuda emare ego senua awa, “Giu. Ema tua nisokare ewa.”
\v 15 Ago senu nukare arero ego sewa awa, “Nu tepo waise. Nu tepo waise. Ni pasinaira witaise.” Ago sewa Pilato meni ego senua awa, “Ema tua nisokare sana ni pasinaira betaise towita?” Ago senu pris babezinoma meni ina ego sewa awa, “Nakare ema tua nasokare zo tepo. Roma emara ema tua Sisa ami gege inoya.”
\v 16 Ago sewa giro Pilato meni ge nusokare niniro Yesu ni pasinaira betaise sero poti wana nusokarera ninua awa.
\s1 Yesu ni pasinaira dewa betenua.
\p 
\v 17 Are soldia meni Yesu puro ni pasinai potiwa dimunu zebu zo zazo nuso Giti Kopira Wetu, ota Yuda gera Goligata, amira puro bamuwa awa.
\v 18 Puro baro ni pasinaira dewa awa. Dero pasina mai eto ni pasinai etora dero zo enibara zo enibara Yesu soe ago urewa dopewa awa.
\v 19 Pilato meni senu Yesura ni pasinaira owe ego ine potiwa awa, “Yesu Nasarete natara. Nu Yuda emara ema tua.”
\v 20 Yesu dewa zebu awa nata itinua amira zorage. Are Yuda ema dainiro meni izima-sauma awinoise owe awa azimuwa. Owe awa Yuda gera ata Roma gera ata Grik gera gaewa awa.
\v 21 Are Yuda emara pris babezinoma meni Pilatore ego sewa awa, “Ni ego gaetesa awa te oko inoya, ‘Yuda emara ema tua.’ Awa doro ego ine gaeyo, ‘Nu nutope na Yuda emara ema tua asinowia.’ Ago gaeyo.”
\v 22 Ago sewa Pilato meni ego senua awa, “Gaetena ami itaise.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 23 Soldia nukare Yesu dero tama woi nuso tame awa zoeto-zoeto, are kanowero pumuwa awa. Ata tama woi tura awa be dara tairo gayai tepo. Ike ena gaero osero bayai awa.
\v 24 Are nukare ego sewa awa, “Awa kapanakai waya wamunoya. Are ozina laki wanakai ema zora nana kei awai giro ami paise.” Ago sero wewa awa. Ago wewa amire ge gayai zo ego itia ami me wenua,
\li2 Nukare tama woi naso tame awa kanowewa.
\li2 Tama woi naso emo ozina laki wewa. Ge gayai ago itinua, are soldia meni ago wewa awa.
\p 
\v 25 Yesura ni pasinai susura ena erama ego ami dopewa: mia nuso, miera zawa, Maria Kliopara ara, Maria nata nuso Madala.
\v 26 Are Yesu nu mia nuso ata bua mai nuso kokopai nuto dopero itiwato giro mia nusore ego senua awa, “Mia, mai niso awa.”
\v 27 Ago sero bua mai nusore ego senua awa, “Mia niso awa.” Ago senu giro be amira ana nu Yesura mia uzumunu nuso nana witinu dia inoisonua awa.
\s1 Yesu betenua.
\p 
\v 28 Are Yesu nu bua nuso tepo wenu giro ge gayai zo itinua awa me waise sero ego senua awa, “Na ou uza inoya.”
\v 29 Ago senu nukare ewara somisomi zo puro ou wain dokaka akou zora itinua amira patiro utura gaero be nusora potiwa ninua awa.
\v 30 Ou wain niro ego senua awa, “Bua wero pesunena.” Ago sero tuma gosumunu ozana nuso tepo wenua awa.
\p 
\v 31 Yuda ema nukare pura nusokarera nena sia inoise giro ego sewa awa, “Auma Betai Daininua amira pura bamubake, are ema ni pasinaira dai awa oko itare.” Ago sero Pilatore ego sewa awa, “Nukare eya betarise sero ni ge sasa soldia meni baro te nusokare dara toumara eya betara woi nusokare ni pasinaira ena parise.” Ago sewa Pilato meni ge nusokare nininua awa.
\v 32 Are soldia nukare pasina ema eto Yesure dai dewa amira zora te wetu dewa toumunu zora da ago dewa toumunu awewa awa.
\v 33 Ago wero Yesura nana baro nu betero itinu giro wetu kaka dai toumamu dowa awa.
\v 34 Ota soldia zo baro karao meni Yesu zezegira ena gaenu urukumunu orarare oure osenua awa.
\p 
\v 35 Nane nena awa giti moka naso meni gina. Are na sero kerenitinona me inoya awa. Na gosinona, ge awa me awa. Nikare dai gawa me waise sero ge me kerenitinona awa.
\v 36 Ge gayai zo ego itia awa me waise sero nena awa kei awenua,
\li2 Nukare wetu nuso zo da di oko dara toumamunoya.
\v 37 Ota ge gayai zo ego itia,
\li2 Nukare nu gaewa urukumunua amira nana giti moka potiro gamunora. Ge gayai eto ago iterato awa.
\s1 Yesu gowewa.
\p 
\v 38 Yosefe Arimatia natara nu Yesura mai zo wero noisonua, ata nu Yuda ema azu wero tuma diai nuso kaka kerenamu bezero puro noisonua. Nune ami Pilato nana baro Yesura woi ni pasinaira ena dusunamu sero atata wenua. Ago wenu Pilato meni nininu baro dusuninua awa.
\v 39 Nikodemo nu gita pire Yesura nana kei awenua ami ni mu zamare mou nuso 34 kilogram ago puro bamuro Yosefe soremunua awa.
\v 40 Ago wero Yesura woi ni mu zamare meni gutero mo kapawai meni ewewato awa. Yuda ema nukare erama betasara ago inoisowa awa.
\v 41 Yesu dewa zebu amira agewara ni bua zo itinua, amira omata so zo bi ditira asero seka wamai itinua. Gita ema zora woi ago kaka potamu.
\v 42 Are Yuda emara pura amira nena sia waira be itinua, noko bi diti awa zorage itinu giro nuto Yesura woi ago potiwato awa.
\c 20
\s1 Yesu seka wero erinua.
\p 
\v 1 Sande pina kaka atiro baitamu Maria nata nuso Madala ami bi ditira bamunua awa. Baro ego ginua awa. Omata bi ditira so be gazai awa dainiro enibara baro itinua.
\v 2 Ago giro sumuro bamuro Simon Petoroto Yesura bua mai kokopaire amira nana kei awero ego senua awa, “Nukare Tuara woi puro baera. Awa nago poteri?”
\v 3 Ago senu giro Petoroto otao nuso zore bamu bi ditira niwato awa.
\v 4 Ebete sumuro susawiseto otao ami Petoro dainiro gita baro bi ditira kei awenua awa.
\v 5 Kei awero omata sora dupuniro mo woi nuso ewewato awa itinu ginua. Ata nu kaka toyamu.
\v 6 Ago inoinu Simon Petoro ama kei awero omata sora toiro mo ginua.
\v 7 Mo zo gitine ewewato awa dai itinu ginua awa. Mo awa mo enire dai oko itinua. Nu imata enibara bozero baitai itinua.
\v 8 Are Petoro meni awa gosinoinu otao nuso gita baro omata sora bera dopenua ami ama toiro ginu me wenua awa.
\v 9 Nuto Yesu betero seka wero eramunoya amira ge gayai itinua awa oko giro baitiwato.
\v 10 Ago weroto nuto noko ewesemuro bamu nate niwato awa.
\s1 Yesu nu Maria nata nuso Madala amira nana kei awenua.
\p 
\v 11 Maria nu bi ditira so be zorage amira dopero di senua awa. Di toise baro omata sora bera dupuniro anegi wenua.
\v 12 Anegi wero angelo eto tama woi kapawaire Yesura zarara itiwato ginua. Zo nu Yesura giti itinua amira zarara, zo Yesura te itinua amira zarara, ago wero itiwato ginua awa.
\v 13 Ginu nuto ego sewato awa, “Ni nogoro di tosi?” Ago sewato nu ego senua awa, “Tua nasora woi puro nago baerata kau inona.”
\v 14 Ago sero kapeteniro Yesu dopero itinu ginua awa. Giro Yesura giti moka kaka giro baitamu wenua awa.
\v 15 Ago wenu Yesu meni atata wero ego senua awa, “Ni nogoro di tosi? Ni are kau inosi?” Ago senu Maria nu ni buara mama meni dopero itinuta asero ego senua awa, “Nine Yesura woi puro baro agewa zora potesita? Se giro baro pumane.”
\v 16 Ago senu Yesu meni ina ego senua awa, “Maria.” Ago senu nu zuzumeniro Yuda gera “Rabonai” asenua. (Ge nasokaira, “Gipai Ema.”)
\v 17 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Na oko ziase. Na Mamera nana kaka witamu awa. Ni baro bua mai nasore ego se: Mama naso awa Mama nisokare. Anutu naso awa Anutu nisokare. Are amira nana witamunona. Ago se gare.”
\v 18 Ago senu Maria nata nuso Madala ami ewesemuro baro Yesura bua mai amire ego senua awa, “Na Tua gena. Nu namore ge awa sesia.” Ago senua awa.
\s1 Yesura bua mai meni so mokara aunitinoiwa nu nusokare
\s1 nana kei awenua.
\p 
\v 19 Sande pi zinu bua mai meni Yuda ema azu wero auniro so be dewa gamunu itiwa Yesu meni nusokare nana soe ena kei awero dopero ego senua awa, “Azu doro kokopai itiwo.”
\v 20 Ago sero boino zara wana etora amire zezegira amire gipenua. Ago wenu bua mai meni Tua nusokare giro yawa sara wewa awa.
\v 21 Ago wewa nu noko numorekare ego senua awa, “Azu doro kokopai itiwo. Mama meni na iyetinua, da ago ine nane nikare iyetitinona.”
\v 22 Ago sero ozana nuso pise nusokare nana niro ego senua awa, “Ozana pumuu.
\v 23 Nikare emara pasina disawa tepo wamunoya. Ota nikare kaka disamu wawa itamunoya.” Ago senua awa.
\s1 Tomasra ge.
\p 
\v 24 Otao nusokare Tomas, zazo nuso zo Didimo, nu awa agewa zora noinu Yesu meni mai enira nana kei awenua.
\v 25 Are otao mai eni meni oziga ge numore ego sewa awa, “Nakare Tua genakare.” Ago sewa nu ego senua awa, “Na natope giti moka naso me meni wanera boino zara giro, o wana sisino naso meni boino zara gaero giro, o zezegi nuso gaitara amira sora wana naso meni sineniro giro awamunona, awa ge nisokare me asamunona.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 26 Waiko be 8 tepo wenu amire bua mai nuso eni ata Tomas dai so mokara toiro so be dapikarago dewa gamunu itiwa Yesu meni nusokare nana soe ena noko kei awero dopero ego senua awa, “Azu doro kokopai itiwo.”
\v 27 Ago sero Tomasre ego senua awa, “Ni wana sisino niso meni wana naso ziro gi. Wana niso sineniro zezegi naso ziro gi. Ago wero duba eto noko oko we. Na seka nona awa gasa me wae.”
\v 28 Ago senu Tomas meni ego senua awa, “Ni Tua naso. Ni Anutu naso.”
\v 29 Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Ni na gosinosa, are ni na tuma didinosa. Nukare na kaka gamu inoise na tuma diamunora nukare ami dai yawa sara wamunora.” Ago senua awa.
\p 
\v 30 Tani eni dainiro Yesu meni bua mai nusora nana giti mokara ena wenua awa na buku emira kaka gaero tepo wamu.
\v 31 Ota ge gainona amira susu nogoro kota, ego emira awa: Nikare ge ei awa azimuro ninitinoise Yesu nu Soyai Ema Kristo, Anutura Mai, amira ge awa gawa me waise, o nu tuma didinoise zazo nuso emo inoise nuai me ewanana tamawise sero ge awa gainona.
\c 21
\s1 Yesura bua mai eni ou ubura noiwa nu nusokare nana kei awenua.
\p 
\v 1 Yesura bua mai eni Taibirias* ou ubura noiwa nu nusokare nana kei awenua. Bua mai dubu ego amira nana kei awenua:
\v 2 Simon Petoro, Tomas zazo nuso zo Didimo, Nataniel Galilaya zebura Kena nata itisonua amira, amire Zebedira mai eto, amire zo eto dai. Ema ago ami poti dara niro itiwa
\v 3 Simon Petoro meni enire ego senua awa, “Na wo pumamu susawena.” Ago senu nukare ego sewa awa, “Nakare nimore dai bayanekai.” Ago sero wara witiro bamuwa awa. Susawise pi amire wo kaka pumamu wewa.
\v 4 Are ou ubura noiwa pina atitinoinu Yesu meni kora dopenua awa. Dopenu nukare benau nuso oko giro baitiwa.
\v 5 Ago wewa Yesu meni nukare atata wero ego senua awa, “Mai awiso, wo nisokare zo itita?” Ago atata wenu nukare ego sewa awa, “Tepo.”
\v 6 Ago sewa nu ego senua awa, “Wa wana mera ana mona potiwo osai wo ikai zumawe.” Ago senu mona potiwa osenu wo dainiro-bake ikewa awa. Ago wewa zumu wara namu kaputiwa awa.
\v 7 Are Yesura bua mai kokopai meni Petorore ego senua awa, “Awa Tua awa.” Ago senu Simon Petoro nu mo gege awero noinua, are nu “Tua noya owa,” awa niniro tama woi nuso tame awa wosuniro ewara dagimunua awa.
\v 8 Nukare kora duku bera asike noiwa, are mai eni meni wa dawinoise mona wore zumuro bamuwa awa.
\v 9 Ago wero ete witiro nena ego ine giwa awa. Niao mokara wore mare sasinoise itinua.
\v 10 Itinu nukare witiro bamuwa Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Wo pumewa amira eni puro muu.”
\v 11 Ago senu Simon Petoro meni wara witiro mona zumu ete ninua awa. Mona mokara wo babezinoma 153 ago itiwa, ata mona oko kapenua.
\v 12 Are Yesu meni numorekare ego senua awa, “Muu, nena nawe.” Ago senu bua mai nuso meni “Ni aweni?” ago atata wamu sero giwa mou wenu giro dowa. Nera kota, nu Tua awa, awa emoko giwa kei awenua awa.
\v 13 Are Yesu meni wo ma bona wero numorekare potinua awa.
\p 
\v 14 Are Yesu nu betaira ena seka wero eriro bua mai nusora nana kei awenu be etorobara wenua awa.
\s1 Yesu meni Petoro be etorobara atata wenua.
\p 
\v 15 Nena niwa amire Yesu meni Simon Petoro atata wero ego senua awa, “Simon Yohanera mai, otao mamai niso nukare na ara tapinowera, awa nine nukare dainitinoise na ara bamu tapinowesa, awa me ni?” Ago senu Petoro meni ina ego senua awa, “Tua, nage otao wero nowenage, awa gosinosa.” Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Ni lama dubu naso awa uninoise noiyo.”
\v 16 Ago sero noko atata wero ego senua awa, “Simon Yohanera mai, ni me na ara tapinowesita?” Ago senu Petoro meni ego senua awa, “Tua, nage otao wero nowenage, awa gosinosa.” Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Ni lama dubu nasora dia wero noiyo.”
\v 17 Ago sero noko atata wero ego senua awa, “Simon Yohanera mia, nage otao wero nowenage, awa me ni?” Tairo nuaira atata wenu be etorobara wenu Petoro nu pumunu nuso nana mou wenu giro duba nitinoise ego senua awa, “Tua, ni nena bamubamu giro tepo inowesa. Nage otao wero nowenage awa gosinosa awa.” Ago senu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Ni lama dubu naso uninoise noiyo.
\v 18 Na me memeka sane. Ni mai seka noise nitope ipu sapi diai niso diro ebata nago nago bayamu susawewesa. Ata noma zai wero wana niso suamasa ema zo meni ipu sapi diai niso diro masi oko bayamu samunosa amira ni puro bayamunoya.”
\v 19 Yesu meni ago toise Petorora betai amira ge awa kereninua. Betai nuso meni Anutura zazo de ike namu inoinua awa senua awa. Ge ago sero numore ego senua awa, “Mu, na ama ganase.”
\v 20 Are Petoro meni zuzumeniro Yesura bua mai kokopai nuso nana atune susaunu ginua. Mai awa gita Betai Daininua amira bona ninoiwa amire Yesu nana zorage baro ge dane potiro atata wero ego senua awa, “Tua, ai meni ni kerenamunoi?”
\v 21 Mai ago senua ami ama susaunu giro Petoro meni Yesu atata wero ego senua awa, “Tua, mai ei awa gire?”
\v 22 Ago atata wenu Yesu meni ego senua awa, “Nu dago nuai na ewesemuro mamu samunona, awa nena awa nena niso oko aewa. Ni na ama gane.” Ago senua awa.
\v 23 Are ge ninai eni meni ama namore ge bisi ego sewa awa, “Mai awa nu oko betamunoya.” Ago toisowa awa. Ata Yesu meni namore ego oko senua, “Nu oko betamunoya.” Ge ego gege senua awa, “Nu dago nuai na ewesemuro mamu samunona, awa nena awa nena niso oko aewa.”
\p 
\v 24 Na nena awa dapikarago giro baitina ami kereniro ge ei awa gaetena. Are nikare namore ego gosinowewa, ge naso me bamubake.
\p 
\v 25 Ota Yesu meni tani eni-kani inoisonua awa. Ota ema meni tani Yesu inoisonua awa da da bukura gayamera, awa buku meni zebu sero topetiro tepo wami, tanita. 
